        "fullLyrics": "[00:00.000] \n[00:34.360] I'll never let you see\n[00:39.540] The way my broken heart is hurting me\n[00:44.910] I've got my pride and I know how to hide\n[00:49.770] All my sorrow and pain\n[00:53.400] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[01:00.820] If I wait for stormy skies\n[01:06.250] You won't know the rain from the tears in my eyes\n[01:10.930] You'll never know that I still love you so\n[01:16.360] Though the heartaches remain\n[01:19.790] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[01:27.340] Raindrops falling from heaven\n[01:31.960] Could never take away my misery\n[01:37.700] But since we're not together\n[01:40.320] I pray for stormy weather\n[01:42.630] To hide these tears I hope you'll never see\n[01:55.058] Someday when my crying's done\n[01:57.618] I'm gonna wear a smile and walk in the sun\n[02:04.238] I may be a fool\n[02:06.238] But till then  darling  you'll never see me complain\n[02:12.348] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[02:49.378] But since we're not together\n[02:51.498] I pray for stormy weather\n[02:53.938] To hide these tears I hope you'll never see\n[02:59.738] Someday when my crying's done\n[03:05.348] I'm gonna wear a smile and walk in the sun\n[03:10.278] I may be a fool\n[03:12.278] But till then  darling  you'll never see me complain\n[03:18.578] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[03:24.258] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[03:29.008] I'll do my crying in the rain\n[03:37.928] I'll do my crying in the rain",
