        "fullLyrics": "[00:06.591] Hello it's me\n[00:12.081] I was wondering if after all these years you'd like to meet\n[00:18.231] To go over everything\n[00:23.790] They say that time's supposed to heal ya but I ain't done much healing\n[00:30.480] Hello can you hear me\n[00:36.350] I'm in california dreaming about who we used to be\n[00:42.180] When we were younger and free\n[00:48.540] I've forgotten how it felt before the world fell at our feet\n[00:54.250] There's such a difference between us\n[01:00.810] And a million miles\n[01:07.410] Hello from the other side\n[01:13.130] I must've called a thousand times to tell you\n[01:20.120] I'm sorry for everything that I've done\n[01:24.550] But when I call you never seem to be home\n[01:31.730] Hello from the outside\n[01:37.320] At least I can say that I've tried to tell you\n[01:44.410] I'm sorry for breaking your heart\n[01:48.670] But it don't matter it clearly doesn't tear you apart anymore\n[02:01.930] Hello how are you\n[02:07.440] It's so typical of me to talk about myself\n[02:12.540] I'm sorry I hope that you're well\n[02:19.550] Did you ever make it out of that town\n[02:23.120] Where nothing ever happened\n[02:25.719] It's no secret\n[02:28.679] That the both of us are running out of time\n[02:38.509] So hello from the other side\n[02:44.299] I must've called a thousand times to tell you\n[02:51.199] I'm sorry for everything that I've done\n[02:55.669] But when I call you never seem to be home\n[03:02.939] Hello from the outside\n[03:08.609] At least I can say that I've tried to tell you\n[03:15.519] I'm sorry for breaking your heart\n[03:19.859] But it don't matter it clearly doesn't tear you apart anymore\n[03:27.088] Ooooohh anymore\n[03:36.038] Ooooohh anymore\n[03:42.097] Ooooohh anymore\n[03:48.017] Anymore\n[03:51.517] Hello from the other side\n[03:57.206] I must've called a thousand times to tell you\n[04:04.265] I'm sorry for everything that I've done\n[04:08.595] But when I call you never seem to be home\n[04:15.825] Hello from the outside\n[04:21.535] At least I can say that I've tried to tell you\n[04:28.444] I'm sorry for breaking your heart\n[04:32.864] But it don't matter it clearly doesn't tear you apart anymore",
