        "fullLyrics": "[00:34.184] We're talking away\n[00:37.159] I don't know what I'm to say\n[00:39.591] I'll say it anyway\n[00:42.766] Today's another day to find you\n[00:46.028] Shying away\n[00:48.867] I'll be coming for your love okay\n[00:51.416] Take on me take on me\n[00:57.091] Take me on take on me\n[01:02.891] I'll be gone\n[01:07.317] In a day or two\n[01:13.557] So needless to say\n[01:16.710] I'm odds and ends\n[01:18.462] But I'll be stumbling away\n[01:22.655] Slowly learning that life is okay\n[01:25.550] Say after me\n[01:28.730] It's no better to be safe than sorry\n[01:31.181] Take on me take on me\n[01:36.810] Take me on take on me\n[01:42.602] I'll be gone\n[01:47.150] In a day or two\n[02:33.118] Oh things that you say\n[02:36.672] Is it life or just to play my worries away\n[02:41.983] You're all the things I've got to remember\n[02:45.233] You're shying away\n[02:48.161] I'll be coming for you anyway\n[02:50.633] Take on me take on me\n[02:56.405] Take me on take on me\n[03:01.974] I'll be gone\n[03:07.021] In a day\n[03:08.494] Take on me take on me\n[03:13.362] Take me on take on me\n[03:18.971] I'll be gone\n[03:23.950] In a day\n[03:29.024] Take on me take on me\n[03:34.650] Take on me take me on\n[03:40.433] Take on me",
