        "fullLyrics": "[00:15.452] Let's dance in style\n[00:16.580] Let's dance for a while\n[00:19.064] Heaven can wait\n[00:20.240] We're only watching skiesthe\n[00:22.602] Hoping for the best\n[00:23.926] But expecting the worst\n[00:25.586] Are you going to drop the bomb or not\n[00:29.438] Let us die young or let us live forever\n[00:32.875] We don't have the power\n[00:34.295] But we never say never\n[00:36.407] Sitting in a sandpit\n[00:38.035] Life is a short trip\n[00:40.047] The music's for the sad men\n[00:43.535] Can you imagine when this race is wrong\n[00:47.027] Turn our golden faces into the sun\n[00:50.555] Praising our leaders\n[00:52.227] We're getting in tune\n[00:53.623] The music's played by the madmen\n[00:57.155] Forever young\n[00:59.327] I want to be forever young\n[01:04.219] Do you really want to live forever\n[01:07.733] Forever and ever\n[01:11.171] Forever young\n[01:13.362] I want to be forever young\n[01:18.203] Do you really want to live forever\n[01:23.382] Forever young\n[01:28.949] Some are like water\n[01:30.264] Some are like the heat\n[01:32.501] Some are a melody and some are the beat\n[01:36.078] Sooner or later\n[01:37.723] They all will be gone\n[01:39.537] Why don't they stay young\n[01:42.787] It's so hard to get old without a cause\n[01:46.495] I don't want to perish like a fading horse\n[01:50.337] Youth's like diamonds in the sun\n[01:53.717] And diamonds are forever\n[01:56.929] So many adventures couldn't happen today\n[02:00.637] So many songs we forgot to play\n[02:04.153] So many dreams swinging out of the blue\n[02:07.581] We'll let them come true\n[02:10.939] Forever young\n[02:13.003] I want to be forever young\n[02:17.908] Do you really want to live forever\n[02:21.335] Forever forever\n[02:24.696] Forever young\n[02:26.992] I want to be forever young\n[02:31.800] Do you really want to live forever\n[02:35.344] Forever and ever\n[02:38.852] Forever young\n[02:41.100] I want to be forever young\n[02:46.009] Do you really want to live forever",
