        "fullLyrics": "[00:13.142] When I find myself in times of trouble\n[00:16.710] Mother Mary comes to me\n[00:19.667] Speaking words of wisdom let it be\n[00:26.040] And in my hour of darkness\n[00:28.481] She is standing right in front of me\n[00:32.419] Speaking words of wisdom let it be\n[00:37.970] Let it be let it be let it be let it be\n[00:45.767] Whisper words of wisdom let it be\n[00:51.971] And when the broken hearted people living in the world agree\n[00:58.544] There will be an answer let it be\n[01:05.005] For though they may be parted\n[01:07.905] There is still a chance that they will see\n[01:11.763] There will be an answer let it be\n[01:17.724] Let it be let it be let it be let it be\n[01:25.145] There will be an answer let it be\n[01:31.433] Let it be let it be let it be let it be\n[01:38.542] Whisper words of wisdom let it be\n[02:25.994] Let it be let it be let it be yeah let it be\n[02:33.898] Whisper words of wisdom let it be\n[02:40.854] And when the night is cloudy\n[02:43.698] There is still a light that shines on me\n[02:47.947] Shine until tomorrow let it be\n[02:54.837] I wake up to the sound of music\n[02:58.313] Mother Mary comes to me\n[03:01.850] Speaking words of wisdom let it be\n[03:07.877] Let it be let it be let it be yeah let it be\n[03:15.668] There will be an answer let it be\n[03:21.873] Let it be let it be let it be yeah let it be\n[03:29.905] There will be an answer let it be\n[03:36.097] Let it be let it be let it be yeah let it be\n[03:43.902] Whisper words of wisdom let it be",
