        "fullLyrics": "[00:08.366] It's a 3 day drive if she drives all night\n[00:12.024] Says she's leavin' at the crack of dawn\n[00:16.213] Well she might still be lyin' here with me\n[00:20.476] But in her heart she's already gone\n[00:24.039] Already packed up the altimas gassed up\n[00:28.205] She's done put the map up there on the dash\n[00:32.543] I'm all tore up just tryin' to man up\n[00:36.483] Dammin' these tears up but can't hold 'em back\n[00:40.679] 'Cause she's in love with California\n[00:45.183] And that west coast sunshine dream\n[00:48.935] These ain't no hollywoods\n[00:51.408] And these hills ain't beverly\n[00:57.639] Ain't no beaches on these backroads\n[01:01.336] No sunset on the boulevard\n[01:05.468] She's in love with California\n[01:09.442] And breakin' my heart\n[01:14.077] Got a waitress job waitin' in an ihop\n[01:18.263] Throw a rock and hit universal city\n[01:22.348] Got a glamour shot in her hip pocket\n[01:26.661] Hopin' somebody'll think she's pretty\n[01:30.199] By this time tomorrow she'll hit Colorado\n[01:34.286] I'll be drownin' my sorrow in a bottle of beam\n[01:38.528] Before she hits flagstaff maybe she'll backtrack\n[01:42.572] But I wouldn't bet that if I was me\n[01:46.885] 'Cause she's in love with California\n[01:51.468] And that west coast sunshine dream\n[01:55.128] These ain't no hollywoods\n[01:57.740] And these hills ain't beverly\n[02:03.373] There ain't no beaches on these backroads\n[02:07.608] No sunset on the boulevard\n[02:11.794] She's in love with California\n[02:15.679] And breakin' my heart\n[02:19.756] Well she was all mine\n[02:24.291] Now it's go time\n[02:28.513] She's in love with California\n[02:32.786] And that west coast sunshine dream\n[02:36.353] These ain't no hollywoods\n[02:39.007] And these hills ain't beverly\n[02:44.639] There ain't no beaches on these backroads\n[02:48.984] No sunset on the boulevard\n[02:52.938] She's in love with California\n[02:56.982] And breakin' my heart\n[03:01.516] She's in love with California\n[03:05.315] And breakin' my heart\n[03:09.265] Oh she's breakin' my heart",
