        "fullLyrics": "[00:08.242] This ain't a song for the broken-hearted\n[00:12.186] Woah oh woah oh oh\n[00:16.047] No silent prayer for the faith-departed\n[00:24.207] I ain't gonna be just a face in the crowd\n[00:27.578] You're gonna hear my voice when I shout it out loud\n[00:33.133] It's my life it's now or never\n[00:39.148] I ain't gonna live forever\n[00:43.117] I just want to live while I'm alive\n[00:49.140] It's my life\n[00:50.980] My heart is like an open highway\n[00:55.021] Like Frankie said \"I did it my way\"\n[00:59.092] I just wanna live while I'm alive\n[01:04.084] It's my life\n[01:14.284] This is for the ones who stood their ground\n[01:22.084] For Tommy and Gina who never backed down\n[01:30.092] Tomorrow's getting harder make no mistake\n[01:34.027] Luck ain't even lucky got to make your own breaks\n[01:39.165] It's my life it's now or never\n[01:45.140] I ain't gonna live forever\n[01:49.131] I just want to live while I'm alive\n[01:55.117] It's my life\n[01:56.925] My heart is like an open highway\n[02:00.877] Like Frankie said \"I did it my way\"\n[02:05.125] I just wanna live while I'm alive\n[02:09.683] 'Cause it's my life\n[02:28.398] Better stand tall when they're calling you out\n[02:31.719] Don't bend don't break baby don't back down\n[02:37.137] It's my life it's now or never\n[02:43.138] I ain't gonna live forever\n[02:47.089] I just want to live while I'm alive\n[02:53.281] It's my life\n[02:54.924] My heart is like an open highway\n[02:58.914] Like Frankie said \"I did it my way\"\n[03:03.122] I just wanna live while I'm alive\n[03:08.097] It's my life\n[03:11.570] And it's now or never\n[03:15.145] I ain't gonna live forever\n[03:19.066] I just want to live while I'm alive\n[03:25.208] It's my life\n[03:27.032] My heart is like an open highway\n[03:30.881] Like Frankie said \"I did it my way\"\n[03:35.176] I just wanna live while I'm alive\n[03:40.160] It's my life",
