        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:17.855] I woke up this morning and the sun was gone\n[00:22.155] Turned on some music to start my day\n[00:26.585] I lost myself in a familiar song\n[00:30.705] I closed my eyes and I slipped away\n[00:51.000] It's more than a feeling\n[00:53.300] More than a feeling\n[00:54.810] When I hear that old song\n[00:56.930] They used to play\n[00:57.930] More than a feeling\n[00:59.310] I begin dreaming\n[01:01.680] More than a feeling\n[01:03.420] 'Til I see Mary Ann walk away  I see my\n[01:10.410] Mary Ann walkin' away\n[01:26.440] So many people have come and gone\n[01:30.750] Their faces fade as the years go byYet\n[01:35.870] I still recall as I wander on\n[01:39.420] As clear as the sun in the summer sky\n[01:59.910] It's more than a feeling\n[02:01.910] More than a feeling When\n[02:03.910] I hear that old song they used to play\n[02:07.530] More than a feeling And\n[02:08.400] I begin dreaming\n[02:11.140] More than a feeling\n[02:12.420] 'Til I see Mary Ann walk away  I see my\n[02:18.800] Mary Ann walkin' away\n[03:04.450] When I'm tired and thinking cold\n[03:08.380] I hide in my music  forget the day\n[03:12.930] And dream of a girl\n[03:15.180] I used to know\n[03:17.370] I closed my eyes and she slipped away\n[03:29.900] She slipped away\n[03:57.335] It's more than a feeling\n[04:00.145] More than a feeling When I\n[04:01.765] Hear that old song they used to play\n[04:05.015] More than a feeling And\n[04:06.325] I begin dreaming\n[04:08.195] More than a feeling'\n[04:09.755] Til I see Mary Ann walk away",
