        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:50.110] Standing in line marking time\n[00:52.050] Waiting for the welfare dime\n[00:55.480] 'Cause they can't buy a job\n[00:58.790] The man in the silk suit hurries by\n[01:00.670] As he catches the poor ladies' eyes\n[01:03.850] Just for fun he says  \"Get a job\"\n[01:09.980] That's just the way it is\n[01:14.280] Some things will never change\n[01:18.650] That's just the way it is\n[01:22.640] Ah but don't you believe them\n[01:32.930] Said  hey little boy you can't go where the others go\n[01:38.360] 'Cause you don't look like they do\n[01:41.660] Said  hey old man how can you stand\n[01:43.980] To think that way  did you really think about it\n[01:47.840] Before you made the rules \n[01:49.850] He said  \"Son  that's just the way it is\n[01:57.340] Some things will never change\n[02:01.760] That's just the way it is\n[02:05.900] Ah but don't you believe them\"\n[03:02.870] That's just the way it is\n[03:06.990] That's just the way it is\n[03:08.480] Well they passed a law in '64\n[03:10.550] To give those who ain't got a little more\n[03:13.470] But it only goes so far\n[03:16.550] Because the law don't change another's mind\n[03:18.790] When all it sees at the hiring time\n[03:22.020] Is the line on the color bar  no  no  no\n[03:28.380] That's just the way it is\n[03:32.370] Some things will never change\n[03:36.870] That's just the way it is\n[03:40.250] That's just the way it is  it is  it is  it is",
