        "fullLyrics": "[00:01.682] Today I don't feel like doing anything\n[00:07.204] I just wanna lay in my bed\n[00:12.419] Don't feel like picking up my phone\n[00:15.219] So leave a message at the tone\n[00:17.759] 'Cause today I swear I'm not doing anything\n[00:23.217] I'm gonna kick my feet up then stare at the fan\n[00:26.356] Turn the TV on throw my hand in my pants\n[00:29.283] Nobody's gonna tell me I can't\n[00:34.237] I'll be lounging on the couch\n[00:35.645] Just chillin' in my Snuggie\n[00:37.335] Click to MTV so they can teach me how to dougie\n[00:39.958] 'Cause in my castle I'm the freaking man\n[00:44.918] Oh oh yes I said it\n[00:47.262] I said it I said it 'cause I can\n[00:51.060] Today I don't feel like doing anything\n[00:56.559] I just wanna lay in my bed\n[01:01.646] Don't feel like picking up my phone\n[01:04.556] So leave a message at the tone\n[01:07.100] 'Cause today I swear I'm not doing anything\n[01:11.655] Nothing at all\n[01:17.232] Nothing at all\n[01:23.665] Tomorrow I'll wake up do some P90X\n[01:26.388] Meet a really nice girl have some really nice sex\n[01:29.426] She's gonna scream out \"This is great\"\n[01:32.640] Oh my god this is great\n[01:33.914] Yeah I might mess around and get my college degree\n[01:37.518] I bet my old man will be so proud of me\n[01:40.170] But sorry pops you'll just have to wait\n[01:45.124] Oh oh yes I said it\n[01:47.632] I said it I said it 'cause I can\n[01:51.276] Today I don't feel like doing anything\n[01:56.883] I just wanna lay in my bed\n[02:02.057] Don't feel like picking up my phone\n[02:04.917] So leave a message at the tone\n[02:07.391] 'Cause today I swear I'm not doing anything\n[02:11.993] No I ain't gonna comb my hair\n[02:15.976] 'Cause I ain't going anywhere\n[02:18.844] No no no no no no no no no\n[02:23.685] I'll just strut in my birthday suit\n[02:26.569] And let everything hang loose\n[02:29.825] Yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah\n[02:31.473] Yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah\n[02:34.312] Oh today I don't feel like doing anything\n[02:40.824] I just wanna lay in my bed\n[02:46.055] Don't feel like picking up my phone\n[02:48.810] So leave a message at the tone\n[02:51.351] 'Cause today I swear I'm not doing anything\n[02:55.940] Nothing at all\n[03:01.373] Nothing at all",
