        "fullLyrics": "[00:16.460] Oh - thinkin' about all our younger years.\n[00:21.890] There was only you and me.\n[00:25.250] We were young and wild and free.\n[00:29.930] Now nothin' can take you away from me.\n[00:35.420] We've been down that road before.\n[00:38.720] But that's over now.\n[00:42.050] You keep mein' back for more.\n[00:46.040] Baby you're all that I want.\n[00:49.010] When you're lyin' here in my arms.\n[00:52.730] I'm findin' it hard to believe.\n[00:55.760] We're in heaven.\n[00:59.630] And love is all that I need.\n[01:02.810] And I found it there in your heart.\n[01:06.650] It isn't too hard to see.\n[01:09.470] We're in heaven.\n[01:23.210] Oh - once in your life you find someone.\n[01:28.850] Who will turn your world around.\n[01:32.150] Bring you up when you're feelin' down.\n[01:36.830] Ya - nothin' could change what you mean to me.\n[01:41.600] Oh there's lots that I could say.\n[01:45.620] But just hold me now.\n[01:48.980] Cause our love will light way.the\n[01:53.060] Baby you're all that I want.\n[01:56.030] When you're lyin' here in my arms.\n[01:59.810] I'm findin' it hard to believe.\n[02:02.780] We're in heaven.\n[02:06.770] And love is all that I need.\n[02:09.980] And I found it there in your heart.\n[02:13.640] It isn't too hard to see.\n[02:16.610] We're in heaven.\n[02:25.340] I've been waitin' for so long.\n[02:29.000] For somethin' to arrive.\n[02:32.450] For love toe along.\n[02:39.020] Now our dreams arein' true.\n[02:42.470] Through the good times and the bad.\n[02:46.640] Ya - I'll be standin' there by you\n[03:04.880] Baby you're all that I want.\n[03:07.880] When you're lyin' here in my arms.\n[03:11.570] I'm findin' it hard to believe.\n[03:14.540] We're in heaven.\n[03:18.410] And love is all that I need.\n[03:21.560] And I found it there in your heart.\n[03:24.680] It isn't too hard to see.\n[03:28.190] We're in heaven.\n[03:30.440] Heaven.........",
