        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:16.930] Look into my eyes you will see\n[00:23.428] What you mean to me\n[00:29.529] Search your heart search your soul\n[00:37.176] And when you find me there you'll search no more\n[00:44.630] Don't tell me it's not worth tryin' for\n[00:51.785] You can't tell me it's not worth dyin' for\n[00:59.039] You know it's true\n[01:02.609] Everything I do I do it for you\n[01:15.375] Look into your heart you will find\n[01:21.615] There's nothing there to hide\n[01:28.084] Take me as I am take my life\n[01:35.924] I would give it all I would sacrifice\n[01:43.220] Don't tell me it's not worth fightin' for\n[01:50.374] I can't help it there's nothing I want more\n[01:57.419] You know it's true\n[02:01.024] Everything I do I do it for you oh yeah\n[02:12.102] There's no love like your love\n[02:19.410] And no other could give more love\n[02:26.726] There's nowhere unless you're there\n[02:33.994] All the time all the way yeah\n[02:54.792] Look into your heart baby\n[03:13.403] Oh you can't tell me it's not worth tryin' for\n[03:21.472] I can't help it there's nothing I want more\n[03:28.675] Yeah I would fight for you I'd lie for you\n[03:36.213] Walk the wire for you yeah I'd die for you\n[03:47.419] You know it's true\n[03:50.771] Everything I do oh I do it for you",
