        "fullLyrics": "[00:15.761] She says her love for me could never die\n[00:23.204] But that'd change if she ever found out about you and I\n[00:30.897] Oh but her love is cold\n[00:34.412] It wouldn't hurt her if she didn't know 'cause\n[00:39.532] When it gets too much I need to feel your touch\n[00:45.000] I'm gonna run to you I'm gonna run to you\n[00:52.525] 'Cause when the feeling's right I'm gonna run all night\n[00:56.224] I'm gonna run to you\n[01:08.874] She's got a heart of gold she'd never let me down\n[01:16.263] But you're the one that always turns me on\n[01:19.230] Keep me coming 'round\n[01:24.034] I know her love is true\n[01:26.843] But it's so damn easy making love to you\n[01:32.337] I got my mind made up I need to feel your touch\n[01:38.066] I'm gonna run to you yeah I'm gonna run to you\n[01:45.753] 'Cause when the feeling's right I'm gonna stay all night\n[01:49.368] I'm gonna run to you yeah\n[01:53.213] I'm gonna run to you oh\n[01:57.259] When the feeling's right I'm gonna run all night\n[02:00.698] I'm gonna run to you\n[02:10.502] When the feeling's right yeah\n[02:19.720] Oh\n[02:41.118] Oh I'm gonna run to you yeah I'm gonna run to you\n[02:50.194] 'Cause when the feeling's right I'm gonna stay all night\n[02:53.800] I'm gonna run to you\n[02:57.104] Oh gonna run to you yeah\n[03:01.664] When the feeling's right I'm gonna stay all night\n[03:06.789] Oh when the feeling's right now\n[03:11.543] Oh yeah when the feeling's right now\n[03:16.725] I'm gonna run to you oh oh yeah\n[03:24.440] Gonna run to you yeah I'm gonna oh\n[03:31.837] I'm gonna run to you run to you\n[03:35.312] Then I'm gonna run to you oh",
