        "fullLyrics": "[00:14.301] I feel like I've been locked up tight\n[00:16.481] For a century of lonely nights\n[00:19.481] Waiting for someone to release me\n[00:24.661] You're licking your lips\n[00:25.911] And blowing kisses my way\n[00:27.531] But that don't mean I'm gonna give it away\n[00:30.211] Baby  Baby  baby （Baby 'baby' baby）\n[00:35.081] Ooh （my body is saying let's go）\n[00:41.791] Ooh （but my heart is saying no）\n[00:47.471] If you wanna be with me\n[00:50.401] Baby there's a price to pay\n[00:52.841] I'm a genie in a bottle\n[00:55.961] You gotta rub me the right way\n[00:58.451] If you wanna be with me\n[01:00.391] I can make your wish come true\n[01:03.821] You gotta make a big impression\n[01:06.691] I gotta like what you do\n[01:08.561] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[01:11.621] You Gotta rub me the right way honey\n[01:14.391] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[01:17.510] Come' come' come on and let me out\n[01:19.330] You just friend and light some low\n[01:21.950] One more dance and then we're good to go\n[01:24.820] Waiting for someone\n[01:27.200] Who needs me\n[01:30.240] Hormones racing at the speed of light\n[01:32.800] But that don't mean it's gotta be tonight\n[01:35.680] Baby' baby' baby （baby' baby' baby）\n[01:38.670] Ooh （my body is saying let's go）\n[01:46.811] Ooh （but my heart is saying no）\n[01:52.051] If you wanna be with me\n[01:55.551] Baby there's a price to pay\n[01:58.301] I'm a genie in a bottle （I'm a genie in a bottle）\n[02:02.781] You gotta rub me the right way\n[02:04.101] If you wanna be with me （Ooh）\n[02:06.901] I can make your wish come true\n[02:09.091] Just come and set me free\n[02:11.841] And I'll be with you\n[02:14.701] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[02:17.081] You Gotta rub me the right way honey\n[02:19.761] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[02:22.571] Come' come' come on and let me out\n[02:25.561] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[02:28.061] You Gotta rub me the right way honey\n[02:30.491] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[02:33.371] Come' come' come on and let me out\n[02:36.111] Ooh （my body is saying let's go）\n[02:41.471] Ooh （but my heart is saying no）\n[02:46.901] If you wanna be with me\n[02:50.021] Baby there's a price to pay\n[02:52.831] I'm a genie in a bottle\n[02:56.071] You gotta rub me the right way\n[02:58.261] If you wanna be with me\n[03:01.011] I can make your wish come true （Ooh）\n[03:04.181] You gotta make a big impression\n[03:06.991] I gotta like what you do （Oh Yeah）\n[03:09.371] If you wanna be with me\n[03:11.921] Baby there's a price to pay\n[03:14.611] I'm a genie in a bottle\n[03:17.791] You gotta rub me the right way\n[03:20.101] If you wanna be with me\n[03:22.390] I can make your wish come true\n[03:25.570] Just come and set me free baby\n[03:29.060] And I'll be with you\n[03:31.120] I'm a genie in a bottle baby\n[03:33.430] Come' come' come' on and let me out",
