        "fullLyrics": "[00:16.201] I know it sounds funny  but I just can't stand the pain\n[00:23.191] Girl  I'm leaving you tomorrow\n[00:30.371] Seems to me girl  you know I've done all I can\n[00:37.981] You see I've begged  stole and I've borrowed （yeah）\n[00:44.511] That's why I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning\n[01:01.171] That's why I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning\n[01:17.711] Why in the world would anybody put chains on me  （yeah）\n[01:23.951] I've paid my dues to make it\n[01:31.821] Everybody wants me to be what they to want me be\n[01:39.801] I'm not happy when I try to fake it  no\n[01:48.791] That's why I'm easy （yeah）  I'm easy like Sunday morning\n[01:56.531] That's why I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning\n[02:18.121] I wanna be high  so high\n[02:25.301] I wanna be free to know the things I do are right\n[02:32.161] I wanna be free  just me  oh baby\n[03:18.331] That's why I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning\n[03:31.621] That's why I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning  whoa\n[03:46.541] Cause I'm easy （woo）  easy like Sunday morning  yeah\n[04:00.641] Cause I'm easy  I'm easy like Sunday morning  whoa",
