        "fullLyrics": "[00:57.549] Here comes Johnny singing oldies goldies\n[01:00.501] Be Bop A Lula baby what I say\n[01:02.922] Here comes Johnny singing I gotta woman\n[01:05.727] Down in the tunnels trying to make it pay\n[01:08.790] He got the action he got the motion\n[01:11.676] Oh yeah the boy can play\n[01:14.649] Dedication devotion\n[01:16.964] Turning all the night time into the day\n[01:19.538] He do the song about the sweet lovin' woman\n[01:22.069] He do the song about the knife\n[01:24.601] Will he do the walk do the walk of life\n[01:29.445] Well he do the walk of life\n[01:42.078] Here comes Johnny and he'll tell you the story\n[01:44.756] Hand me down my walkin' shoes\n[01:47.511] Here comes Johnny with the power and the glory\n[01:50.677] Backbeat the talkin' blues\n[01:53.316] He got the action he got the motion\n[01:56.547] Yeah oh yeah the boy can play\n[01:58.928] Dedication devotion\n[02:01.222] It's turning all the night time into the day\n[02:04.167] The song about the sweet lovin' woman\n[02:06.559] He do the song about the knife\n[02:09.089] And he do the walk he do the walk of life\n[02:13.932] Yeah do the walk of life\n[02:29.942] Woo woo woo\n[02:37.649] Here comes Johnny singing oldies goldies\n[02:40.668] Be Bop A Lula baby what I say\n[02:43.117] Here comes Johnny singing I gotta woman\n[02:45.825] Down in the tunnels trying to make it pay\n[02:48.945] He got the action he got the motion\n[02:51.727] Oh yeah yeah the boy can play\n[02:54.603] Dedication devotion\n[02:56.950] It's turning all the night time into the day\n[02:59.735] And after all the violence and double talk\n[03:02.201] There's just a song in all the trouble and the strife\n[03:04.905] You do the walk yeah you do the walk of life\n[03:09.611] Yeah you do the walk of life\n[03:14.743] Woo woo woo\n[03:32.708] Woo woo woo\n[03:43.763] Woo woo woo\n[03:48.190] Woo woo woo\n[03:54.886] Woo woo woo",
