        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:16.05] Well, I'm running down the road\n[00:19.11] Tryin' to loosen my load\n[00:20.88] I've got seven women on my mind\n[00:23.87] Four that wanna own me\n[00:25.87] Two that wanna stone me\n[00:27.48] One says she's a friend of mine\n[00:30.63] Take it easy\n[00:33.61] Take it easy\n[00:36.74] Don't let the sound of your own wheels\n[00:40.21] Drive you crazy\n[00:43.93] Lighten up while you still can\n[00:47.03] Don't even try to understand\n[00:50.84] Just find a place to make your stand\n[00:53.24] And take it easy\n[00:57.43] \n[00:59.92] Well, I'm standing on a corner\n[01:03.47] In Winslow, Arizona\n[01:05.08] And such a fine sight to see\n[01:07.46] It's a girl, my Lord, in a flatbed Ford\n[01:11.89] Slowin' down to take a look at me\n[01:14.78] Come on, baby, don't say maybe\n[01:20.96] I gotta know if your sweet love\n[01:25.08] Is gonna save me\n[01:28.64] We may lose, and we may win\n[01:31.83] Though we will never be here again\n[01:35.73] So open up, I'm climbin' in\n[01:38.29] So take it easy\n[01:42.90] \n[02:09.87] Well, I'm running down the road\n[02:12.35] Trying to loosen my load\n[02:14.57] Got a world of trouble on my mind\n[02:17.35] Lookin' for a lover\n[02:19.85] Who won't blow my cover\n[02:21.60] She's so hard to find\n[02:23.56] Take it easy\n[02:27.31] Take it easy\n[02:30.88] Don't let the sound of your own wheels\n[02:34.03] Make you crazy\n[02:36.98] Come on, baby, don't say maybe\n[02:43.01] I gotta know if your sweet love\n[02:47.34] Is gonna save me\n[02:51.96] \n[03:02.32] Oh, we got it easy\n[03:09.11] \n[03:15.91] We oughta take it easy\n[03:20.36]",
