        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:11.070] Walking down 29th and park\n[00:16.530] I saw you in another's arms\n[00:21.960] Only a month we've been apart\n[00:26.340] You look happier\n[00:32.820] Saw you walk inside a bar\n[00:37.980] He said something to make you laugh\n[00:43.380] I saw that both your smiles were twice as wide as ours\n[00:47.130] Yeah, you look happier, you do\n[00:53.370] Ain't nobody hurt you like I hurt you\n[00:58.530] But ain't nobody love you like I do\n[01:03.930] Promise that I will not take it personal, baby\n[01:09.540] If you're moving on with someone new\n[01:13.170] 'Cause baby you look happier, you do\n[01:18.360] My friends told me one day I'll feel it too\n[01:23.910] And until then I'll smile to hide the truth\n[01:29.130] But I know I was happier with you\n[01:36.720] Sat in the corner of the room\n[01:42.090] Everything's reminding me of you\n[01:46.950] Nursing an empty bottle and telling myself you're happier\n[01:53.730] Aren't you?\n[01:57.420] Ain't nobody hurt you like I hurt you\n[02:02.460] But ain't nobody need you like I do\n[02:08.040] I know that there's others that deserve you\n[02:12.750] But my darling, I am still in love with you\n[02:17.190] But I guess you look happier, you do\n[02:22.290] My friends told me one day I'll feel it too\n[02:28.020] I could try to smile to hide the truth\n[02:33.180] But I know I was happier with you\n[03:00.030] Baby, you look happier, you do\n[03:05.190] I knew one day you'd fall for someone new\n[03:10.440] But if he breaks your heart like lovers do\n[03:15.750] Just know that I'll be waiting here for you",
