        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:02.652] I found a love for me\n[00:10.653] Darling just dive right in and follow my lead\n[00:18.237] Well I found a girl beautiful and sweet\n[00:25.752] Oh I never knew you were the someone waiting for me\n[00:32.668] Cause we were just kids when we fell in love\n[00:36.968] Not knowing what it was I will not give you up this time\n[00:48.346] But darling just kiss me slow your heart is all I own\n[00:55.915] And in your eyes you're holding mine\n[01:02.748] Baby I'm dancing in the dark with you between my arms\n[01:14.145] Barefoot on the grass listening to our favourite song\n[01:21.206] When you said you looked a mess I whispered underneath my breath\n[01:28.400] But you heard it darling you look perfect tonight\n[01:41.770] Well I found a woman stronger than anyone I know\n[01:49.059] She shares my dreams I hope that someday I'll share her home\n[01:56.797] I found a love to carry more than just my secrets\n[02:04.810] To carry love to carry children of our own\n[02:11.230] We are still kids but we're so in love fighting against all odds\n[02:19.314] I know we'll be alright this time\n[02:27.085] Darling just hold my hand be my girl I'll be your man\n[02:34.398] I see my future in your eyes\n[02:41.277] Baby I'm dancing in the dark with you between my arms\n[02:52.645] Barefoot on the grass listening to our favourite song\n[02:59.468] When I saw you in that dress looking so beautiful\n[03:05.342] I don't deserve this darling you look perfect tonight\n[03:26.856] Baby I'm dancing in the dark with you between my arms\n[03:37.948] Barefoot on the grass listening to our favourite song\n[03:44.988] I have faith in what I see\n[03:48.378] Now I know I have met an angel in person\n[03:54.746] And she looks perfect I don't deserve this\n[04:02.468] You look perfect tonight",
