        "fullLyrics": "[00:14.430] I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[00:17.471] Baby imma have the best f**king night of my life\n[00:21.032] And wherever it takes me I'm down for the ride\n[00:24.758] Baby don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[00:29.474] Cos I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[00:32.527] Baby imma have the best f**king night of my life\n[00:36.141] And wherever it takes me I'm down for the ride\n[00:39.874] Baby don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[00:55.559] Don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[01:01.608] You know I'm down for whatever tonight\n[01:05.539] I don't need the finer things in life\n[01:09.187] No matter where I go it's a good time\n[01:14.576] And I I don't need to sit in VIP\n[01:20.555] Middle of the floor that's where I'll be\n[01:24.198] Don't got a lot but that's enough for me\n[01:29.488] Cos I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[01:32.509] Baby imma have the best f**king night of my life\n[01:36.248] And wherever it takes me I'm down for the ride\n[01:39.801] Baby don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[01:59.743] I'm good\n[02:03.707] Good\n[02:07.058] I'm good\n[02:10.231] Don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[02:14.229] So I just let it go let it go oh na na na\n[02:17.925] No I don't care no more care no more oh na na na\n[02:21.716] So come on let me know let me know\n[02:23.835] Put your hands up na na na\n[02:25.503] No baby nothings gonna stop us tonight\n[02:29.268] Cos I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright\n[02:32.308] Baby imma have the best f**king night of my life\n[02:35.934] And wherever it takes me I'm down for the ride\n[02:39.780] Baby don't you know I'm good yeah I'm feeling alright",
