        "fullLyrics": "[00:24.994] When lights go down I see no reason\n[00:31.853] For you to cry we've been through this before\n[00:39.123] In every time in every season\n[00:45.913] God knows I've tried so please don't ask for more\n[00:55.272] Can't you see it in my eyes\n[00:59.380] Though this might be our last goodbye\n[01:07.719] Carrie Carrie things they change my friend whoa\n[01:21.537] Carrie Carrie maybe we'll meet again somewhere again\n[01:44.067] I read your mind with no intentions\n[01:51.287] Of being unkind I wish I could explain\n[01:58.375] It all takes time a whole lot of patience\n[02:05.385] If it's a crime how come I feel no pain\n[02:14.555] Can't you see it in my eyes\n[02:18.733] Though this might be our last goodbye\n[02:24.162] Oh oh oh\n[02:27.022] Carrie Carrie oh things they change my friend whoa\n[02:40.792] Carrie Carrie maybe we'll meet again\n[03:17.975] Oh can't you see it in my eyes\n[03:25.475] This might be our last goodbye\n[03:31.174] Oh oh oh\n[03:33.053] Oh Carrie Carrie\n[03:40.743] Oh oh things they change\n[03:45.143] Carrie Carrie Carrie\n[03:47.003] Whoa\n[03:47.503] Carrie Carrie maybe we'll meet again oh somewhere again\n[04:13.732] When lights go down",
