        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:14.670] I gotta take a little time\n[00:19.340] A little time to think things over\n[00:27.790] I better read between the lines\n[00:32.230] In case I need it when I'm older\n[00:41.230] Now\n[00:50.220] This mountain I must climb\n[00:54.790] Feels like the world upon my shoulders\n[01:00.710] Through the clouds I see love shine\n[01:04.930] It keeps me warm as life grows colder\n[01:10.670] In my life there's been heartache and pain\n[01:17.420] I don't know if I can face it again\n[01:23.540] Can't stop now I've travelled so far\n[01:28.811] To change this lonely life\n[01:35.861] I want to know what love is\n[01:42.181] I want you to show me\n[01:47.871] I want to feel what love is\n[01:54.151] I know you can show me\n[02:00.621] Oh oh\n[02:09.191] I'm gonna take a little time\n[02:13.581] A little time to look around me\n[02:19.381] I've got nowhere left to hide\n[02:23.611] It looks like love has finally found me\n[02:28.751] In my life there's been heartache and pain\n[02:36.311] I don't know if I can face it again\n[02:42.191] Can't stop now I've travelled so far\n[02:47.561] To change this lonely life\n[02:54.551] I want to know what love is\n[03:00.471] I want you to show me\n[03:06.411] I want to feel what love is\n[03:12.691] I know you can show me\n[03:18.251] I want to know what love is\n[03:24.111] I want you to show me\n[03:29.811] I want to feel what love is\n[03:36.371] I know you can show me\n[03:42.811] Let's talk about love\n[03:45.121] I want to know what love is\n[03:48.501] The love that you feel inside\n[03:51.191] I want you to show me\n[03:54.041] And I'm feeling so much love\n[03:56.541] I want to feel what love is\n[03:59.741] No you just can't hide\n[04:02.611] I know you can show me\n[04:11.361] I want to know what love is\n[04:15.251] (Let's talk about love)\n[04:17.241] I know you can show me\n[04:23.191] I want to know what love is\n[04:28.291] I know you can show me\n[04:37.601] I want to know what love is\n[04:40.291] I want to know\n[04:43.991] I want you to show me",
