        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:33.750] So long, I've been looking too hard\n[00:40.290] I've been waiting too long\n[00:43.290] Sometimes I don't know what I will find\n[00:48.090] I only know it's a matter of time\n[00:52.500] When you love someone, when you love someone\n[01:01.860] It feels so right, so warm and true\n[01:06.840] I need to know if you feel it too\n[01:12.600] Maybe I'm wrong, won't you tell me if I'ming on too strong\n[01:20.730] This heart of mine has been hurt before,\n[01:25.740] this time I wanna be sure\n[01:29.580] I've been waiting for a girl like you toe into my life\n[01:39.180] I've been waiting for a girl like you, your loving will survive\n[01:48.750] I've been waiting for someone new to make me feel alive\n[01:58.290] Yeah, waiting for a girl like you to coming into my life\n[02:19.200] You're so good, when we make love it's understood\n[02:27.660] It's more than a touch or a word can say\n[02:32.670] Only in dreams could it be this way\n[02:37.590] When you love someone, yeah, really love someone\n[02:47.730] Now I know it's right, from the moment I wake up till deep in the night\n[02:56.070] There's nowhere on earth that I'd rather be than holding you tenderly\n[03:04.980] I've been waiting for a girl like you toe into my life\n[03:14.550] I've been waiting for a girl like you, your loving will survive\n[03:24.120] I've been waiting for someone new to make me feel alive\n[03:33.630] Yeah, waiting for a girl like you to coming into my life\n[03:54.630] I've been waiting, waiting for you,\n[04:11.630] ooh, I've been waiting\n[04:16.110] I've been waiting\n[04:19.950] （I've been waiting for a girl like you, I've been waiting）\n[04:30.870] Won't youe into my life?",
