        "fullLyrics": "[00:38.760] Well I guess it would be nice\n[00:41.310] If I could touch your body\n[00:43.920] I know not everybody\n[00:46.200] Has got a body like you\n[00:48.870] But I've got to think twice\n[00:51.420] Before I give my heart away\n[00:53.910] And I know all the games you play\n[00:56.190] Because I play them too\n[00:58.620] Oh but I\n[00:59.760] Need some time off from that emotion\n[01:04.770] Time to pick my heart up off the floor\n[01:08.850] oh when that love comes down without devotion\n[01:14.520] Well it takes a strong man baby\n[01:16.770] But I'm showing you the door\n[01:18.900] 'Cause I gotta have faith\n[01:29.460] Baby !\n[01:31.440] I know you're asking me to stay\n[01:33.810] Say please,please,please,don't go away\n[01:36.270] You say I'm giving you the blues\n[01:38.490] Maybe\n[01:41.340] You mean every word you say\n[01:43.680] Can't help but think of yesterday\n[01:46.500] And another who tied me down to loverboy rules\n[01:49.680] Before this river\n[01:52.080] Becomes an ocean\n[01:54.810] Before you throw my heart back on the floor\n[01:58.350] Oh baby I reconsider\n[02:02.070] My foolish notion\n[02:04.620] Well I need someone to hold me\n[02:06.840] But I'll wait for something more\n[02:09.000] Yes I've gotta have faith\n[02:39.840] Before this river\n[02:42.210] Becomes an ocean\n[02:44.940] Before you throw my heart back on the floor\n[02:48.480] Oh baby I reconsider\n[02:52.170] My foolish notion\n[02:54.750] Well I need someone to hold me\n[02:56.970] But I'll wait for something more\n[03:01.620] 'Cause I gotta have faith",
