        "fullLyrics": "[00:19.746] Talk to me softly\n[00:22.335] There's something in your eyes\n[00:27.566] Don't hang your head in sorrow\n[00:31.227] And please don't cry\n[00:35.080] I know how you feel inside I've\n[00:38.781] I've been there before\n[00:42.817] Something's changin' inside you\n[00:46.520] And don't you know\n[00:50.496] Don't you cry tonight\n[00:54.359] I still love you baby\n[00:58.110] Don't you cry tonight\n[01:05.856] Don't you cry tonight\n[01:09.267] There's a heaven above you baby\n[01:13.237] And don't you cry tonight\n[01:21.133] Give me a whisper\n[01:24.797] And give me a sigh\n[01:28.741] Give me a kiss before you\n[01:32.544] Tell me goodbye\n[01:36.528] Don't you take it so hard now\n[01:39.848] And please don't take it so bad\n[01:44.091] I'll still be thinkin' of you\n[01:47.578] And the times we had baby\n[01:53.710] And don't you cry tonight\n[02:01.635] Don't you cry tonight\n[02:09.331] Don't you cry tonight\n[02:12.748] There's a heaven above you baby\n[02:16.852] And don't you cry tonight\n[02:55.442] And please remember that I never lied\n[03:03.345] And please remember\n[03:06.751] How I felt inside now honey\n[03:10.908] You gotta make it your own way\n[03:14.610] But you'll be alright now sugar\n[03:19.013] You'll feel better tomorrow\n[03:22.427] Come the morning light now baby\n[03:26.612] And don't you cry tonight\n[03:34.388] And don't you cry tonight\n[03:42.057] And don't you cry tonight\n[03:45.591] There's a heaven above you baby\n[03:49.696] And don't you cry\n[03:53.345] Don't you ever cry\n[03:57.733] Don't you cry tonight\n[04:01.559] Baby maybe someday\n[04:05.383] Don't you cry\n[04:08.815] Don't you ever cry\n[04:13.335] Don't you cry\n[04:15.621] Tonight",
