        "fullLyrics": "[00:31.611] Mama take this badge from me\n[00:38.411] I can't use it anymore\n[00:47.081] It's getting dark too dark to see\n[00:53.011] Feels like I'm knockin' on heaven's door\n[01:00.751] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[01:07.931] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[01:15.111] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[01:22.281] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[01:59.531] Mama put my guns in the ground\n[02:06.461] I can't shoot them anymore\n[02:13.821] That cold black cloud is comin' down\n[02:21.111] Feels like I'm knockin' on heaven's door\n[02:29.411] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[02:35.771] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[02:43.141] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[02:51.311] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door\n[03:46.911] YOU JUST BETTER START SNIFFIN YOUR OWN\n[03:48.281] RANK SUBJUGATION JACK 'CAUSE IT'S JUST\n[03:49.721] YOU AGAINST YOUR LIBIDO  THE TATTERED BANK\n[03:51.531] AND THE MORTICIAN  FOREVER MAN AND IT\n[03:53.271] WOULDN'T BE LUCK IF YOU COULD GET OUT OF\n[03:54.891] LIFE ALIVE\n[03:55.521] Knock-knock-knockin' on heaven's door",
