        "fullLyrics": "[00:46.275] She got a smile that it seems to me\n[00:49.705] Reminds me of childhood memories\n[00:53.533] Where everything was as fresh as the bright blue sky\n[01:01.559] Now and then when I see her face\n[01:04.767] She takes me away to that special place\n[01:08.472] And if I stared too long\n[01:10.716] I'd probably break down and cry\n[01:16.582] Oh Sweet child of mine\n[01:24.192] Oh oh oh oh Sweet love of mine\n[01:47.693] She got eyes of the blue sky\n[01:51.009] As if they thought of rain\n[01:55.085] I hate to look into those eyes\n[01:58.577] And see an ounce of pain\n[02:02.771] Her hair reminds me of a warm safe place\n[02:06.328] Where as a child I'd hide\n[02:10.331] And pray for the thunder\n[02:12.691] And the rain\n[02:13.896] To quietly pass me by\n[02:18.164] Oh oh oh sweet child of mine\n[02:24.760] Oh oh oh oh sweet love of mine\n[03:04.522] Oh oh oh oh sweet child of mine\n[03:12.122] Oh oh oh oh sweet love of mine\n[03:20.270] Oh oh oh oh sweet child of mine\n[03:28.268] Oh sweet love of mine\n[04:39.385] Where do we go\n[04:40.730] Where do we go now\n[04:42.735] Where do we go\n[04:46.603] Where do we go\n[04:48.316] Where do we go\n[04:50.097] Where do we go now\n[04:53.890] Where do we go\n[04:56.080] Sweet child\n[04:57.576] Where do we go now\n[05:03.416] Where do we go\n[05:05.178] Where do we go now\n[05:09.108] Where do we go\n[05:12.743] Where do we go now\n[05:16.499] Where do we go\n[05:20.237] Where do we go now\n[05:24.025] Where do we go\n[05:27.647] Where do we go now now now now now now now now\n[05:32.735] Sweet child\n[05:34.601] Sweet child of mine",
