        "fullLyrics": "[01:14.477] When I look into your eyes\n[01:17.776] I can see a love restrained\n[01:27.185] But darlin' when I hold you\n[01:30.425] Don't you know I feel the same\n[01:35.457] Yeah\n[01:39.772] 'Cause nothing lasts forever\n[01:42.732] And we both know hearts can change\n[01:51.988] And it's hard to hold a candle\n[01:54.949] In the cold November rain\n[02:04.536] We've been through this such a long long time\n[02:07.344] Just tryna kill the pain ooh yeah\n[02:15.264] But lovers always come and lovers always go\n[02:18.237] And no one's really sure who's lettin' go today walkin' away\n[02:27.759] If we could take the time to lay it on the line\n[02:30.579] I could rest my head just knowin' that you were mine all mine\n[02:41.559] So if you want to love me\n[02:44.710] Then darlin' don't refrain\n[02:53.894] Or I'll just end up walkin'\n[02:56.839] In the cold November rain\n[03:04.247] Do you need some time on your own\n[03:10.311] Do you need some time all alone\n[03:16.340] Ooh everybody needs some time on their own\n[03:21.925] Ooh don't you know you need some time all alone\n[03:30.134] I know it's hard to keep an open heart\n[03:36.085] When even friends seem out to harm you\n[03:41.942] But if you could heal a broken heart\n[03:48.122] Wouldn't time be out to charm you woah-woah\n[04:44.033] Sometimes I need some time on my own\n[04:50.057] Sometimes I need some time all alone\n[04:55.609] Ooh everybody needs some time on their own\n[05:02.241] Ooh don't you know you need some time all alone\n[05:38.113] And when your fears subside\n[05:40.909] And shadows still remain ooh yeah\n[05:50.244] I know that you can love me\n[05:52.935] When there's no one left to blame\n[06:02.263] So never mind the darkness\n[06:05.383] We still can find a way\n[06:14.214] 'Cause nothin' lasts forever\n[06:17.062] Even cold November rain\n[07:36.575] Don't ya think that you need somebody\n[07:39.167] Don't ya think that you need someone\n[07:41.927] Everybody needs somebody\n[07:44.583] You're not the only one you're not the only one\n[07:49.786] Don't ya think that you need somebody\n[07:52.376] Don't ya think that you need someone\n[07:55.091] Everybody needs somebody\n[07:57.737] You're not the only one you're not the only one\n[08:02.875] Don't ya think that you need somebody\n[08:05.505] Don't ya think that you need someone\n[08:08.161] Everybody needs somebody\n[08:10.882] You're not the only one you're not the only one\n[08:15.977] Don't ya think that you need somebody\n[08:18.633] Don't ya think that you need someone\n[08:21.514] Everybody needs somebody",
