        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:11.869] I hear the ticking of the clock\n[00:14.999] I'm lying here the room's pitch dark\n[00:22.569] I wonder where you are tonight\n[00:26.009] No answer on the telephone\n[00:33.129] And the night goes by so very slow\n[00:38.259] Oh I hope that it won't end though\n[00:43.819] Alone\n[00:50.609] Till now I always got by on my own\n[00:56.499] I never really cared until I met you\n[01:01.169] And now it chills me to the bone\n[01:06.249] How do I get you alone\n[01:11.319] How do I get you alone\n[01:20.769] You don't know how long I have wanted\n[01:24.129] To touch your lips and hold you tight  oh\n[01:31.128] You don't know how long I have waited\n[01:34.758] And I was going to tell you tonight\n[01:41.688] But the secret is still my own\n[01:46.758] And my love for you is still unknown\n[01:52.268] Alone\n[02:10.098] Till now I always got by on my own\n[02:15.948] I never really cared until I met you\n[02:22.128] And now it chills me to the bone\n[02:25.808] How do I get you alone\n[02:31.268] How do I get you alone\n[02:36.268] GUITAR SOLO\n[02:58.756] How do I get you alone\n[03:04.106] How do I get you alone\n[03:09.096] Alone  alone",
