        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:00.457] Halfway To Hell - Jelly Roll\n[00:22.077] Yeah\n[00:23.791] I'm a county jail revival I'm a bottle and a Bible\n[00:28.024] I'm a rolling stone disciple with a cross across my face\n[00:32.507] I'm a trailer park tornado jagged edges on my halo\n[00:37.052] Hope the chariot gon' swing low and carry me away\n[00:41.791] This little light of mine damn near burned me alive\n[00:46.123] Lord knows that mama tried and I don't know if I'm\n[00:50.174] Halfway to Heaven or halfway to Hell\n[00:54.413] My angels and demons at war with myself\n[00:58.854] One foot in the fire and I still can't tell\n[01:03.277] Am I halfway to Heaven\n[01:05.909] Halfway to Heaven or Hell\n[01:10.614] I'm a dive bar Sunday sermon holy water with my bourbon\n[01:15.159] Standin' on a bridge I'm burnin' with a can of gasoline\n[01:19.336] Am I worth savin' if I'm always faded\n[01:23.685] It feels like I'm caught in-between\n[01:28.383] Halfway to Heaven or halfway to Hell\n[01:32.523] My angels and demons at war with myself\n[01:37.014] One foot in the fire and I still can't tell\n[01:41.401] Am I halfway to Heaven\n[01:44.041] Halfway to Heaven or Hell\n[01:56.027] This little light of mine damn near burned me alive\n[01:59.998] Lord knows that mama tried and I don't know if I'm\n[02:04.217] Halfway to Heaven or halfway to Hell\n[02:08.440] My angels and demons at war with myself\n[02:13.210] Halfway to Heaven or halfway to Hell\n[02:17.423] My angels and demons at war with myself\n[02:21.887] One foot in the fire and I still can't tell\n[02:26.255] Am I halfway to Heaven\n[02:28.916] Halfway to Heaven or Hell\n[02:38.016] Halfway to Heaven or Hell",
