        "fullLyrics": "[00:09.162] What would I do without your smart mouth\n[00:12.901] Drawing me in and you kicking me out\n[00:16.583] You've got my head spinning no kidding I can't pin you down\n[00:24.345] What's going on in that beautiful mind\n[00:28.068] I'm on your magical mystery ride\n[00:31.857] And I'm so dizzy don't know what hit me but I'll be alright\n[00:40.415] My head's under water but I'm breathing fine\n[00:48.123] You're crazy and I'm out of my mind\n[00:53.874] 'Cause all of me loves all of you\n[01:00.232] Love your curves and all your edges\n[01:04.291] All your perfect imperfections\n[01:08.182] Give your all to me\n[01:11.778] I'll give my all to you\n[01:15.550] You're my end and my beginning\n[01:19.525] Even when I lose I'm winning\n[01:23.042] 'Cause I give you all of me\n[01:30.860] And you give me all of you\n[01:40.597] How many times do I have to tell you\n[01:44.321] Even when you're crying you're beautiful too\n[01:47.965] The world is beating you down I'm around\n[01:53.754] Through every mood\n[01:55.729] You're my downfall you're my muse\n[01:59.360] My worst distraction my rhythm and blues\n[02:03.155] I can't stop singing it's ringing in my head for you\n[02:11.916] My head's under water but I'm breathing fine\n[02:19.685] You're crazy and I'm out of my mind\n[02:25.302] 'Cause all of me loves all of you\n[02:31.729] Love your curves and all your edges\n[02:35.585] All your perfect imperfections\n[02:39.619] Give your all to me\n[02:43.251] I'll give my all to you\n[02:47.062] You're my end and my beginning\n[02:50.833] Even when I lose I'm winning\n[02:54.410] 'Cause I give you all of me\n[03:02.279] And you give me all of you\n[03:09.520] Give me all of you\n[03:13.216] Cards on the table we're both showing hearts\n[03:20.828] Risking it all though it's hard\n[03:26.219] 'Cause all of me loves all of you\n[03:32.709] Love your curves and all your edges\n[03:36.602] All your perfect imperfections\n[03:40.474] Give your all to me\n[03:44.082] I'll give my all to you\n[03:48.165] You're my end and my beginning\n[03:52.058] Even when I lose I'm winning\n[03:55.552] 'Cause I give you all of me\n[04:03.068] And you give me all of you\n[04:11.131] I give you all of me\n[04:18.416] And you give me all of you",
