        "fullLyrics": "[00:22.852] If you wanna roll me\n[00:25.288] Then you gotta roll me all night long\n[00:33.009] And if you wanna use me\n[00:35.568] Then you gotta use me till I'm gone\n[00:44.759] I'm not a fallen angel I just fell behind\n[00:49.695] I'm out of luck and I'm out of time\n[00:55.007] If you don't wanna love me let me go\n[01:00.119] I'm runnin' for the last train\n[01:02.534] I'm runnin' for the last train home\n[01:14.623] If you wanna know me\n[01:16.842] Then you gotta know me through and through\n[01:20.726] Da-da-da da-da\n[01:23.294] Da-da-da da-da\n[01:24.717] And if you're gonna hurt me\n[01:27.164] Then you gotta hold me next to you\n[01:30.988] Da-da-da da-da\n[01:33.623] Da-da-da da-da\n[01:36.237] No matter how you work it things go wrong\n[01:41.348] I put my heart where it don't belong\n[01:46.588] So if you're comin' with me let me know\n[01:51.765] Maybe you're the last train\n[01:54.364] Maybe you're the last train home\n[01:57.115] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[01:59.540] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:02.090] And I surrender and I surrender\n[02:07.491] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:10.098] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:12.577] And I surrender and I surrender\n[02:17.851] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:20.386] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:23.034] And I surrender and I surrender\n[02:28.114] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:30.689] I'm on the last train runnin'\n[02:33.283] And I surrender and I surrender\n[02:41.046] Oh-yeah\n[02:44.545] Oh-uh-uh-uh-uh-uh",
