        "fullLyrics": "[00:28.320] Someone i know is staring at me\n[00:33.540] And when i look into her eyes\n[00:37.530] I see a girl that i used to be\n[00:41.070] I hardly recognise\n[00:44.550] Cos in the space of a year\n[00:47.610] I've watched the old me disappear\n[00:51.660] All of the things i once held precious\n[00:55.200] Just don't mean anything anymore\n[00:58.710] Cos suddenly\n[01:00.480] You came, and changed the way i feel\n[01:05.220] No one could love you more\n[01:07.800] Because you came and turned my life around\n[01:13.260] No one could take your place\n[01:16.800] I've never felt good with permanent things\n[01:21.570] Now i don't want anything to change\n[01:25.860] You can't imagine the joy you bring\n[01:29.400] My life won't be the same\n[01:33.000] And i'll be there when you call\n[01:36.030] I'll pick you up if you should fall\n[01:40.020] Cos i have never felt such inspiration\n[01:44.790] Nobody else ever gave me more because\n[01:48.870] You came, and changed the way i feel\n[01:53.640] No one could love you more\n[01:56.190] Because you came and turned my life around\n[02:01.680] No one could take your place\n[02:21.390] I watch you sleep in the still of the night\n[02:26.340] You look so pretty when you dream\n[02:30.330] So many people just go through life\n[02:34.170] Holding back, they don't say what they mean\n[02:39.990] But it's easy for me\n[02:44.670] Since you came\n[02:50.100] No one could love you more\n[02:52.680] Because you came and turned my life around\n[02:58.170] No one could take your place\n[03:01.440] You came, and changed the way i feel\n[03:06.210] No one could love you more\n[03:08.790] Because you came and turned my life around\n[03:14.250] No one could take your place\n[04:05.970] You can",
