        "fullLyrics": "[00:37.023] Hey yeah\n[00:40.513] Hey yeah\n[00:45.420] I'm going nowhere\n[00:48.160] Gotta face up to it\n[00:49.780] Gotta wake up to it\n[00:52.650] I feel so guilty\n[00:55.340] Killing time is a sin\n[00:57.150] There's no way you can win\n[00:59.640] A dam burst of dreams flows thru' me\n[01:03.010] They'll show me where I could be\n[01:07.010] Flash point feelings flow\n[01:10.690] Thru' my mind moving\n[01:14.430] From the mountains to the sea\n[01:17.430] I'll run across this land\n[01:21.790] Looking out for strength and beauty\n[01:24.850] A diamond in the sand\n[01:29.100] I will chase the four winds over\n[01:32.220] Trying to understand\n[01:36.400] I won't stop until I'm holding\n[01:39.270] Heaven in my hands\n[01:50.810] I won't let nobody\n[01:53.740] Turn me off of the track\n[01:55.680] Now there's no turning back\n[01:58.290] Won't let no worries\n[02:00.800] Turn my head inside out\n[02:02.610] Now there's no room for doubt\n[02:05.600] I'm heading for my destiny\n[02:09.340] And it feels electric to me\n[02:12.340] Flash point feelings go\n[02:16.400] Thru' my mind\n[02:20.160] I was lonely goin' nowhere\n[02:23.390] Drowning on dry land\n[02:27.380] I was almost stranded there\n[02:30.120] A shipwreck on the sand\n[02:34.630] But now I'll chase the whole world over\n[02:37.880] Making my demands\n[02:41.870] And I won't stop until I'm holding\n[02:44.990] Heaven in my hands\n[02:48.850] Aah aaa\n[02:55.590] Hey yeah\n[03:18.800] From the mountains to the sea\n[03:21.180] I'll run across this land\n[03:25.977] Looking out for strength and beauty\n[03:28.847] A diamond in the sand\n[03:33.157] And I will chase the four winds over\n[03:36.217] Trying to understand\n[03:40.397] And I won't stop until I'm holding\n[03:43.517] Heaven in my hands\n[03:47.757] I was lonely going nowhere\n[03:50.877] Drowning on dry land\n[03:55.057] I was almost stranded there\n[03:57.877] A ship wreck on the sand",
