        "fullLyrics": "[00:31.890] Our dad\n[00:33.060] Would send us to our room\n[00:34.620] Hed be the voice of doom\n[00:36.900] He said that we would thank him later\n[00:39.570] All day\n[00:40.350] He was solid as a rock\n[00:42.480] But by eight oclock\n[00:44.340] Wed be crumbling\n[00:47.250] One night\n[00:48.450] My brother joe meand\n[00:49.950] Climbed down the family tree\n[00:52.290] That grew outside our bedroom window\n[00:54.930] We ran\n[00:55.770] Though we knew it couldnt last\n[00:57.870] Running from the past\n[00:59.790] From things that we were born to be\n[01:02.670] Looking back its so bizarre\n[01:04.830] It runs in the family\n[01:07.920] All the things we are\n[01:10.380] On the back seat of the car\n[01:12.480] With joseph and emily\n[01:15.330] We only see so far\n[01:18.660] - and we all have our daddys eyes\n[01:21.870] Looking back its so bizarre\n[01:41.070] Dad rang\n[01:42.270] The officer in charge\n[01:44.250] A man so large\n[01:46.110] He barely fit his circumstances\n[01:49.140] He said\n[01:49.770] Two kids out on the street\n[01:51.510] Were picked up on the beat\n[01:53.460] And in the station\n[01:56.190] So theres me\n[01:57.660] With emily and joe\n[01:59.370] Daddy driving home\n[02:01.530] All heading in the same direction\n[02:04.140] He knew\n[02:05.130] No matter what the breaks\n[02:06.870] Wed make the same mistakes\n[02:08.940] Couldnt take his eyes of mejoe and\n[02:11.880] Looking back its so bizarre\n[02:14.040] It runs in the family\n[02:17.130] All the things we are\n[02:19.590] On the backseat of the car\n[02:21.720] With joseph and emily\n[02:24.540] We only see so far\n[02:27.870] - and we all have our daddys eyes\n[02:31.140] Looking back its so bizarre\n[02:33.240] It runs in the family\n[02:36.330] All the things we are\n[02:38.700] Looking back its so bizarre\n[02:41.700] Like a dream within a dream\n[02:43.410] Were all somewhere in between\n[02:49.350] Like a drummer plays his drum\n[02:51.060] Like a father like a son\n[02:57.120] - and your gonna have to face the music\n[03:01.140] - face the music\n[03:11.580] Hey hey\n[03:16.950] We keep it running in familythe\n[03:19.710] Hey hey\n[03:24.660] We keep it coming in the family\n[03:29.430] hey hey\n[03:32.370] We keep it coming in the family\n[03:37.140] hey hey\n[03:40.080] We keep it coming in the family\n[03:46.110] Looking back its so bizarre\n[03:48.270] It runs in the family\n[03:51.330] All the things we are\n[03:53.790] On the backseat of the car\n[03:55.920] With joseph and emily\n[03:58.770] We only see so far\n[04:02.070] - cause we all have our daddys eyes\n[04:05.310] Take me back into your arms\n[04:07.320] Its no longer a mystery\n[04:10.290] No cause for alarm\n[04:13.020] Could have never come this far\n[04:15.120] With no sense of history\n[04:18.000] It always leaves a scar\n[04:21.300] - and we all have our daddys eyes\n[04:24.540] Looking back its bizarreso\n[04:27.240] Running in the family\n[04:37.440] Running in the family\n[04:40.650] and we all have our daddys eyes\n[04:43.740] looking back its so bizzre\n[05:04.530] running in the family\n[05:12.060] running in the family\n[05:17.070] Hey, hey!\n[05:19.860] running in the family\n[05:24.780] heyhey,\n[05:27.540] running in the family\n[05:47.010] end",
