        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:16.522] No one knows what it's like\n[00:19.620] To be the bad man\n[00:23.380] To be the sad man\n[00:27.583] Behind blue eyes\n[00:32.127] And no one knows\n[00:33.334] What it's like to be hated\n[00:39.543] To be faded to telling only lies\n[00:47.351] But my dreams they aren't as empty\n[00:55.369] As my conscious seems to be\n[01:03.305] I have hours only lonely\n[01:11.243] My love is vengeance\n[01:12.515] That's never free\n[01:24.084] No one knows what its like\n[01:27.001] To feel these feelings\n[01:30.822] Like i do and i blame you\n[01:39.941] No one bites back as hard\n[01:43.462] On their anger\n[01:46.930] None of my pain woe\n[01:51.114] Can show through\n[01:55.207] But my dreams they aren't as empty\n[02:03.198] As my conscious seems to be\n[02:11.149] I have hours only lonely\n[02:18.885] My love is vengeance\n[02:22.413] That's never free\n[02:31.584] Discover l i m p say it x4\n[02:40.005] No one knows what its like\n[03:06.843] To be mistreated to be defeated\n[03:15.647] Behind blue eyes\n[03:19.728] No one know how to say\n[03:23.148] That they're sorry and don't worry\n[03:30.881] I'm not telling lies\n[03:35.042] But my dreams they aren't as empty\n[03:43.008] As my conscious seems to be\n[03:50.979] I have hours only lonely\n[03:58.591] My love is vengeance\n[04:02.603] That's never free\n[04:11.815] No one knows what its like\n[04:15.023] To be the bad man to be the sad man\n[04:23.251] Behind blue eyes",
