        "fullLyrics": "[00:32.836] Holiday celebrate\n[00:41.009] Holiday celebrate\n[00:49.058] If we took a holiday\n[00:53.123] Took some time to celebrate\n[00:57.256] Just one day out of life\n[01:01.279] It would be it would be so nice\n[01:05.738] Everybody spread the word\n[01:09.722] Were gonna have a celebration\n[01:15.128] All across the world\n[01:18.943] In every nation\n[01:23.054] It's time for the good times\n[01:27.120] Forget about the bad times oh yeah\n[01:30.192] One day to come together\n[01:31.816] To release the pressure\n[01:35.279] We need a holiday\n[01:38.106] If we took a holiday\n[01:42.126] Took some time to celebrate\n[01:46.524] Just one day out of life\n[01:50.330] It would be it would be so nice\n[02:11.046] You can turn this world around\n[02:15.117] And bring back all of those happy days\n[02:20.445] Put your troubles down\n[02:24.284] It's time to celebrate\n[02:28.570] Let love shine\n[02:32.436] And we will find\n[02:35.495] A way to come together\n[02:37.533] And make things better\n[02:40.597] We need a holiday\n[02:43.863] If we took a holiday\n[02:47.429] Took some time to celebrate\n[02:51.545] Just one day out of life\n[02:55.726] It would be it would be so nice\n[03:16.200] Holiday celebrate\n[03:24.210] Holiday celebrate\n[03:32.554] If we took a holiday\n[03:36.582] Took some time to celebrate\n[03:40.645] Just one day out of life\n[03:44.621] It would be it would be so nice\n[03:48.740] Holiday",
