        "fullLyrics": "[00:53.647] I have a tale to tell\n[01:02.320] Sometimes it gets so hard to hide it well\n[01:12.251] I was not ready for the fall\n[01:19.823] Too blind to see the writing on the wall\n[01:29.033] A man can tell a thousand lies\n[01:32.912] I've learned my lesson well\n[01:36.307] Hope I live to tell the secret I have learned\n[01:41.703] Till then it will burn inside of me\n[02:05.732] I know where beauty lives\n[02:14.366] I've seen it once I know the warm she gives\n[02:24.238] The light that you could never see\n[02:31.847] It shines inside you can't take that from me\n[02:40.889] A man can tell a thousand lies\n[02:44.804] I've learned my lesson well\n[02:48.173] Hope I live to tell the secret I have learned\n[02:53.566] Till then it will burn inside of me\n[03:04.942] The truth is never far behind\n[03:09.093] You've kept it hidden well\n[03:12.116] If I live to tell the secret I knew then\n[03:17.713] Will I ever have the chance again\n[03:41.134] If I ran away \n[03:43.862] I'd never have the strength to go very far\n[03:49.885] How would they hear the beating of my heart\n[03:58.758] Will it grow cold\n[04:01.369] The secret that I hide\n[04:05.089] Will I grow old\n[04:07.274] How will they hear\n[04:09.424] When will they learn\n[04:11.528] How will they know\n[04:25.792] A man can tell a thousand lies\n[04:29.662] I've learned my lesson well\n[04:32.876] Hope I live to tell the secret I have learned\n[04:38.227] Till then it will burn inside of me\n[04:49.600] The truth is never far behind\n[04:53.821] You kept it hidden well\n[04:56.909] If I live to tell the secret I knew then\n[05:02.429] Will I ever have the chance again\n[05:13.669] A man can tell a thousand lies\n[05:17.491] I've learned my lesson well\n[05:21.003] Hope I live to tell the secret I have learned\n[05:26.483] Till then it will burn inside of me",
