        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:10.363] Beauty queen of only eighteen\n[00:14.089] She had some trouble with herself\n[00:19.729] He was always there to help her\n[00:23.657] She always belonged to someone else\n[00:29.472] I drove for miles and miles\n[00:32.265] And wound up at your door\n[00:38.794] I've had you so many times\n[00:41.783] But somehow I want more\n[00:47.951] I don't mind spending every day\n[00:52.356] Out on your corner in the pouring rain\n[00:57.035] Look for the girl with the broken smile\n[01:02.053] Ask her if she wants to stay a while\n[01:05.300] And she will be loved\n[01:10.046] And she will be loved\n[01:18.250] Tap on my window knock on my door\n[01:22.364] I want to make you feel beautiful\n[01:27.641] I know I tend to get so insecure\n[01:32.712] Doesn't matter anymore\n[01:37.658] It's not always rainbows and butterflies\n[01:40.864] It's compromise that moves us along yeah\n[01:46.434] My heart is full and my door's always open\n[01:50.343] You come any time you want yeah\n[01:56.235] I don't mind spending every day\n[02:00.585] Out on your corner in the pouring rain\n[02:05.299] Look for the girl with the broken smile\n[02:10.291] Ask her if she wants to stay a while\n[02:13.502] And she will be loved\n[02:18.286] And she will be loved\n[02:22.882] And she will be loved\n[02:27.620] And she will be loved\n[02:34.038] I know where you hide\n[02:36.422] Alone in your car\n[02:38.767] Know all of the things that make you who you are\n[02:43.418] I know that goodbye means nothing at all\n[02:47.650] Comes back and makes me catch her every time she falls yeah\n[02:57.025] Tap on my window knock on my door\n[03:01.145] I want to make you feel beautiful\n[03:06.886] I don't mind spending every day\n[03:11.290] Out on your corner in the pouring rain oh\n[03:16.003] Look for the girl with the broken smile\n[03:20.898] Ask her if she wants to stay a while\n[03:24.239] And she will be loved\n[03:28.945] And she will be loved\n[03:33.634] And she will be loved\n[03:38.430] And she will be loved\n[03:53.953] I don't mind spending every day\n[03:58.345] Out on your corner in the pouring rain\n[04:02.878] Please don't try so hard to say goodbye",
