        "fullLyrics": "[00:29.562] She was more like a beauty queen from a movie scene\n[00:33.313] I said \"Don't mind but what do you mean I am the one\n[00:38.695] Who will dance on the floor in the round\"\n[00:43.807] She said I am the one\n[00:46.978] Who will dance on the floor in the round\n[00:53.929] She told me her name was Billie Jean\n[00:56.523] As she caused a scene\n[00:58.026] Then every head turned with eyes that dreamed of bein' the one\n[01:03.393] Who will dance on the floor in the round\n[01:10.128] People always told me \"Be careful of what you do\n[01:13.968] Don't go around breakin' young girls' hearts\"\n[01:17.041] Hee-hee\n[01:18.138] And mother always told me \"Be careful of who you love\n[01:22.021] And be careful of what you do\n[01:23.452] Oh-oh\n[01:24.236] 'Cause the lie becomes the truth\"\n[01:25.386] Oh-oh\n[01:25.851] Hey-ay\n[01:26.951] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[01:30.845] She's just a girl who claims that I am the one\n[01:35.132] Oh baby\n[01:36.172] But the kid is not my son hoo\n[01:41.069] She says I am the one\n[01:43.278] Oh baby\n[01:44.160] But the kid is not my son\n[01:47.414] Hee-hee-hee no-no-no hee-hee-hee\n[01:50.580] Hoo\n[01:51.525] For forty days and for forty nights the law was on her side\n[01:55.474] But who can stand when she's in demand\n[01:58.262] Her schemes and plans\n[02:00.814] 'Cause we danced on the floor in the round hee\n[02:05.713] So take my strong advice just remember to always think twice\n[02:13.083] Don't think twice\n[02:14.081] Do think twice\n[02:15.276] A-hoo\n[02:15.988] She told my baby we'd danced till three then she looked at me\n[02:19.969] Then showed a photo of a baby cryin' his eyes were like mine\n[02:24.430] Oh no\n[02:25.434] 'Cause we danced on the floor in the round baby\n[02:29.973] Ooh hee-hee-hee\n[02:32.206] People always told me \"Be careful of what you do\n[02:35.806] And don't go around breakin' young girls' hearts\"\n[02:39.026] Don't break no hearts\n[02:39.878] Hee-hee\n[02:40.200] But she came and stood right by me\n[02:41.991] Just the smell of sweet perfume\n[02:43.676] Ha-oh\n[02:44.173] This happened much too soon\n[02:45.635] Ha-oh ha-ooh\n[02:46.362] She called me to her room\n[02:47.467] Ha-oh hoo\n[02:47.979] Hey-ay\n[02:48.876] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[02:52.229] Hoo\n[02:52.781] She's just a girl who claims that I am the one\n[02:58.075] But the kid is not my son\n[03:01.650] No-no-no no-no-no-no-no-no\n[03:04.460] Hoo\n[03:05.321] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[03:09.228] She's just a girl who claims that I am the one\n[03:13.563] Oh baby\n[03:14.484] But the kid is not my son\n[03:18.203] Oh no no\n[03:19.503] She says I am the one\n[03:21.594] Oh baby\n[03:22.647] But the kid is not my son\n[03:27.004] No hee-hee\n[03:28.079] Ah hee-hee-hee\n[03:30.883] Hee hoo\n[03:44.030] She says I am the one but the kid is not my son\n[03:50.670] No-no-no hoo\n[03:53.418] Ouw\n[03:54.435] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[03:58.300] She's just a girl who claims that I am the one\n[04:02.351] You know what you did to me baby\n[04:03.721] But the kid is not my son\n[04:06.613] No-no-no no-no-no-no\n[04:08.046] No-no-no no-no-no\n[04:08.999] She says I am the one\n[04:11.613] But the kid is not my son\n[04:14.982] No-no-no-no\n[04:16.838] She says I am the one\n[04:19.015] You know what you did\n[04:20.901] She says he is my son\n[04:22.972] Breakin' my heart babe\n[04:25.017] She says I am the one\n[04:27.286] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[04:31.253] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[04:35.374] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[04:37.987] She is just a girl\n[04:39.395] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[04:42.124] She is just a girl\n[04:42.834] Don't call me Billie Jean\n[04:43.664] Billie Jean is not my lover\n[04:46.242] She is just a girl\n[04:47.154] Hoo she's not at the scene\n[04:48.037] Billie Jean is not\n[04:49.412] Hee aaow ooh\n[04:51.746] Billie Jean is",
