        "fullLyrics": "[00:10.820] Looking out across the nighttime\n[00:16.071] The city winks a sleepless eye\n[00:20.928] Hear her voice shake my window\n[00:26.648] Sweet seducing sighs\n[00:31.325] Get me out into the nighttime\n[00:36.738] Four walls won't hold me tonight\n[00:41.635] If this town is just an apple\n[00:47.114] Then let me take a bite\n[00:50.962] If they say why why why why\n[00:54.506] Tell them that it's human nature\n[00:56.994] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[01:01.248] If they say why why why why\n[01:04.789] Tell them that it's human nature\n[01:07.436] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[01:12.516] Reaching out to touch a stranger\n[01:18.123] Electric eyes are everywhere\n[01:22.829] See that girl she knows I'm watching\n[01:28.293] She likes the way I stare\n[01:32.272] If they say why why why why\n[01:35.738] Just tell them that it's human nature\n[01:38.336] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[01:42.513] If they say why why why why\n[01:44.861] She's giving in by keeping him a'round\n[01:46.149] Tell them that it's human nature\n[01:48.660] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[01:53.445] I like livin' this way\n[01:56.037] I like lovin' this way\n[02:03.710] That way\n[02:04.898] Why oh why\n[02:08.866] That way\n[02:09.986] Why oh why\n[02:14.684] Looking out across the morning\n[02:19.899] The city's heart begins to beat\n[02:24.770] Reaching out I touch her shoulder\n[02:30.226] I'm dreaming of the street\n[02:34.120] If they say why why why why\n[02:37.671] Tell them that it's human nature\n[02:40.303] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[02:44.423] If they say why why why why\n[02:45.948] She's giving in by keeping him a'round\n[02:48.547] Ooh-ooh tell 'em\n[02:50.745] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[02:54.744] If they say why why why why why why\n[02:58.340] Cha-da-cha-sha-sha-sha-sha-sha aah-ah\n[03:01.241] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[03:05.017] If they say why why why why why why why\n[03:06.924] She's giving in by keeping him a'round\n[03:09.382] Ooh-ooh tell 'em aah-ah\n[03:12.429] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[03:15.349] If they say why why why why why why\n[03:19.330] Ooh tell 'em\n[03:21.826] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[03:25.962] If they say why why why why\n[03:27.026] She's giving in by keeping him a'round\n[03:29.430] Da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da\n[03:31.923] Why why why why does he do me that way\n[03:36.651] I like living this way\n[03:39.087] Why oh why\n[03:44.097] That way\n[03:44.792] Why oh why\n[03:49.337] That way\n[03:49.854] Why oh why\n[03:54.414] That way",
