        "fullLyrics": "[00:04.980] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[00:14.619] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[00:18.779] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[00:23.509] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[00:28.349] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[00:33.058] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[00:38.818] Here we go gettin' smooth to the groove\n[00:40.918] Watchin' lovely ladies as I swoo with as I move\n[00:43.317] Cause that's what they say But I can't prove\n[00:45.656] So turn it up again and watch me move to the groove\n[00:48.166] As we get close you whisper \"coco\"\n[00:50.456] I hold you in my arms and you say \"jamboo\"\n[00:53.006] Scream and shout, turn and say \"columbo\"\n[00:55.395] Now I gotta go so coco\n[00:56.945] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[01:01.815] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[01:06.685] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[01:11.435] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[01:16.985] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[01:21.595] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[01:25.685] Hey yor\n[01:26.555] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[01:31.305] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[01:35.505] Hey yor\n[01:45.825] That's the way I treat the girls kinda smooth see\n[01:47.835] Cause there's one man that and yo! that's me see\n[01:50.495] So let me show you 'round as you sip your tee gee\n[01:52.815] But no coco loco boom while I take a Tea leaf\n[01:55.325] When I hold my baby tighter she says I do it nicer\n[01:57.685] I like my chicken with rice and lemonada\n[02:00.145] And that's whatshe gets when she shouts out jamboo\n[02:02.495] Now I gotta go you coco\n[02:04.495] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[02:09.035] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[02:13.855] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[02:18.644] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[02:24.124] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:28.914] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:33.754] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:38.544] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:43.363] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:48.133] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[02:52.573] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[02:57.103] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[03:01.983] Put me up, put me down, Put my feet back on the ground\n[03:06.623] Put me up, take / feel my heart and make me happy\n[03:12.113] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[03:16.883] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[03:21.703] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[03:26.433] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah\n[03:31.333] Ya ya ya coco jamboo Ya ya yeah...",
