        "fullLyrics": "[00:12.798] Usually these ol' neon lights\n[00:15.798] Are pretty good for bad goodbyes\n[00:18.868] They got some girls off of my mind\n[00:22.188] But baby not tonight\n[00:24.128] Cause I've been putting in overtime\n[00:27.168] Trying to get over your leaving\n[00:30.228] You're still right here on my mind\n[00:32.898] You sure did a number on me\n[00:35.528] I've tried jack I've tried jim\n[00:38.488] I've tried every last one of them\n[00:41.188] Ol' heartbreak bottles up on that shelf\n[00:44.138] But the burn don't work and the buzz don't help\n[00:47.338] Been taking these shots shots shots\n[00:50.446] 80 90 everything they've got\n[00:53.858] But the whiskey don't kill likе it's supposed to do\n[00:57.208] Baby your memory must be bulletproof\n[01:06.848] There ain't no way I'm driving home\n[01:09.918] I'm three sheets done tied one on\n[01:12.918] But this liquor ain't as strong\n[01:15.868] As your sweet love is\n[01:17.578] I've tried jack I've tried jim\n[01:20.508] I've tried every last one of them\n[01:23.188] Ol' heartbreak bottles up on that shelf\n[01:26.128] But the burn don't work and the buzz don't help\n[01:29.338] Been taking these shots shots shots\n[01:32.118] 80 90 everything they've got\n[01:35.858] But the whiskey don't kill like it's supposed to do\n[01:39.198] Baby your memory must be bulletproof\n[01:42.988] All my favorite country songs\n[01:45.978] Guess they must've got it wrong\n[01:48.858] Cause I'm still here and you ain't gone\n[01:51.938] You ain't gone baby\n[02:05.368] I've tried jack I've tried jim\n[02:08.468] I've tried every last one of them\n[02:11.168] Ol' heartbreak bottles up on that shelf\n[02:14.118] But the burn don't work and the buzz don't help\n[02:17.358] Been taking these shots shots shots\n[02:20.128] 80 90 everything they've got\n[02:23.878] But the whiskey don't kill like it's supposed to do\n[02:27.198] Baby your memory must be bulletproof\n[02:31.078] All my favorite country songs\n[02:33.968] Guess they must've got it wrong\n[02:36.848] Cause I'm still here and you ain't gone\n[02:39.868] You ain't gone baby\n[02:44.734] Oh oh you ain't gone baby\n[02:51.228] Baby your memory must be bulletproof",
