        "fullLyrics": "[00:22.014] You would not believe your eyes\n[00:24.533] If ten million fireflies\n[00:27.221] Lit up the world as I fell asleep\n[00:32.581] 'Cause they'd fill the open air\n[00:35.189] And leave teardrops everywhere\n[00:37.397] You'd think me rude but I would just stand and stare\n[00:43.237] I'd like to make myself believe\n[00:47.171] That planet Earth turns slowly\n[00:53.305] It's hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep\n[00:58.736] 'Cause everything is never as it seems\n[01:04.466] 'Cause I'd get a thousand hugs\n[01:07.089] From ten thousand lightning bugs\n[01:09.625] As they tried to teach me how to dance\n[01:15.190] A foxtrot above my head\n[01:17.838] A sock hop beneath my bed\n[01:19.920] The disco ball is just hanging by a thread\n[01:26.081] I'd like to make myself believe\n[01:29.952] That planet Earth turns slowly\n[01:36.050] It's hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep\n[01:41.454] 'Cause everything is never as it seems\n[01:45.625] When I fall asleep\n[01:49.860] Leave my door open just a crack\n[01:52.794] Please take me away from here\n[01:55.125] 'Cause I feel like such an insomniac\n[01:58.376] Please take me away from here\n[02:00.751] Why do I tire of counting sheep\n[02:03.651] Please take me away from here\n[02:05.982] When I'm far too tired to fall asleep\n[02:09.283] Haha\n[02:11.337] To ten million fireflies\n[02:13.876] I'm weird 'cause I hate goodbyes\n[02:16.283] I got misty eyes as they said farewell\n[02:19.575] Said farewell\n[02:21.816] But I'll know where several are\n[02:24.234] If my dreams get real bizarre\n[02:26.489] 'Cause I saved a few and I keep them in a jar\n[02:30.219] Jar jar jar\n[02:32.690] I'd like to make myself believe\n[02:36.762] That planet Earth turns slowly\n[02:42.626] It's hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep\n[02:47.931] 'Cause everything is never as it seems\n[02:52.407] When I fall asleep\n[02:53.896] I'd like to make myself believe\n[02:57.857] That planet Earth turns slowly\n[03:04.032] It's hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep\n[03:09.365] 'Cause everything is never as it seems\n[03:13.710] When I fall asleep\n[03:15.369] I'd like to make myself believe\n[03:19.240] That planet Earth turns slowly\n[03:25.520] It's hard to say that I'd rather stay awake when I'm asleep\n[03:30.773] Because my dreams are bursting at the seams",
