        "chorus": "Am F G Am 2x | Dm G Em Am 2x",
        "chorusCue": "",
        "chorusTitle": "VERSE",
        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:01.181] (All day  all day)\n[00:02.750] (All day  all day)\n[00:40.301] I don't know why  I don't know how\n[00:44.791] I thought I loved you  but I'm not sure now\n[00:48.971] I've seen you look at strangers too many times\n[00:53.341] A love-you-once is of a  a different kind\n[00:57.651] Remember when we felt the sun\n[01:02.011] A love like paradise  how hot it burned\n[01:06.501] A threat of distant thunder  the sky was red\n[01:10.751] And when you walked  you always - turned every head\n[01:15.241] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[01:19.491] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[01:23.731] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[01:28.221] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[01:41.592] I thought that when we fought I was to blame\n[01:45.962] But now I know you play a different game\n[01:50.142] I've watched you dance with danger  still wanting more\n[01:54.572] Add another number to the score\n[01:58.382] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[02:03.122] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[02:07.122] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[02:11.862] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[02:17.352] When you look around you wonder\n[02:19.472] Do you play to win \n[02:21.472] Or are you just a bad loser \n[02:42.431] (All day  all day)\n[02:48.120] (All day  all day)\n[02:51.736] I don't know why  I don't know how\n[02:55.606] I'd thought I loved you  but I'm not sure now\n[02:59.906] I hear the thunder crashing  the sky is dark\n[03:04.276] And now a storm is breaking within my heart\n[03:08.456] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[03:12.886] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[03:16.946] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[03:21.626] (All day  all day  domino dancing)\n[03:25.961] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[03:30.261] (All day  all day  domino dancing)\n[03:34.071] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[03:39.011] (All day  all day) Domino dancing\n[03:43.381] (All day  all day) Watch them all fall down\n[03:47.821] (All day  all day)",
