        "fullLyrics": "[00:44.930] When I look back upon my life\n[00:48.580] It's always with a sense of shame\n[00:52.360] I've always been the one to blame\n[01:01.800] For everything I long to do\n[01:05.520] No matter when or where or who\n[01:09.360] Has one thing in common too\n[01:13.330] It's a it's a it's a it's a sin\n[01:20.740] It's a sin\n[01:25.160] Everything I've ever done\n[01:26.860] Everything I ever do\n[01:28.750] Everyplace I've ever been\n[01:30.770] Everywhere I'm going to\n[01:33.530] It's a sin\n[01:35.810] At school they taught me how to be\n[01:39.530] So pure in thought and word and deed\n[01:43.810] They didn't quite succeed\n[01:50.920] For everything I long to do\n[01:54.570] No matter when or where or who\n[01:58.480] Has one thing in common too\n[02:02.450] It's a it's a it's a it's a sin\n[02:09.810] It's a sin\n[02:14.220] Everything I've ever done\n[02:15.920] Everything I ever do\n[02:17.810] Everyplace I've ever been\n[02:19.820] Everywhere I'm going to\n[02:22.530] It's a sin\n[02:24.800] Father forgive me I tried not to do it\n[02:31.940] Turned over a new leaf then tore right through it\n[02:39.510] Whatever you taught me I didn't believe it\n[02:47.220] Father you fought me cause I didn't care\n[02:51.230] And I still don't understand\n[02:58.900] So I look back upon my life\n[03:02.620] Forever with a sense of shame\n[03:06.520] I've always been the one to blame\n[03:15.910] For everything I long to do\n[03:19.690] No matter when or where or who\n[03:23.400] Has one thing in common too\n[03:27.360] It's a it's a it's a it's a sin\n[03:34.730] It's a sin\n[03:39.130] Everything I've ever done\n[03:40.960] Everything I ever do\n[03:42.860] Everyplace I've ever been\n[03:44.800] Everywhere I'm going to\n[03:47.510] It's a sin\n[04:01.500] It's a it's a it's a it's a sin\n[04:18.500] It's a it's a it's a it's a sin",
