        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:11.605] When I'm feeling blue\n[00:15.146] All I have to do\n[00:18.030] Is take a look at you\n[00:21.802] Then I'm not so blue\n[00:25.151] When you're close to me\n[00:28.441] I can feel your heart beat\n[00:31.707] I can hear you breathing near my ear\n[00:38.446] Wouldn't you agree\n[00:41.742] Baby you and me got a groovy kind of love\n[00:51.759] Anytime you want to you can turn me onto\n[00:58.480] Anything you want to\n[01:01.762] Anytime at all\n[01:05.147] When I kiss your lips\n[01:08.441] Ooh I start to shiver\n[01:11.731] Can't control the quivering inside\n[01:18.427] Wouldn't you agree\n[01:21.706] Baby you and me got a groovy kind of love oh\n[02:05.126] When I'm feeling blue\n[02:08.354] All I have to do\n[02:11.242] Is take a look at you\n[02:14.988] Then I'm not so blue\n[02:18.306] When I'm in your arms\n[02:21.635] Nothing seems to matter\n[02:25.055] My whole world could shatter I don't care\n[02:31.668] Wouldn't you agree\n[02:35.045] Baby you and me got a groovy kind of love\n[02:43.818] We got a groovy kind of love\n[02:50.366] We got a groovy kind of love oh\n[03:10.405] We got a groovy kind of love",
