        "chorus": "D A D A | C G C G",
        "chorusCue": "",
        "chorusTitle": "Block 2",
        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:08.032] Hello?\n[00:08.517] (Hello hello hello)\n[00:10.253] Is there anybody in there?\n[00:14.285] Just nod if you can hear me\n[00:18.837] Is there anyone home?\n[00:22.962] Come on\n[00:23.486] (Come on come on)\n[00:24.542] Now\n[00:26.022] I hear you're feeling down\n[00:30.206] Well I can ease your pain\n[00:33.011] And get you on your feet again\n[00:38.165] Relax\n[00:38.869] (Relax relax relax)\n[00:40.804] I'll need some information first\n[00:45.670] Just the basic facts\n[00:48.931] Can you show me where it hurts?\n[00:53.686] There is no pain you are receding\n[01:01.215] A distant ship smoke on the horizon\n[01:08.614] You are only coming through in waves\n[01:15.673] Your lips move but I can't hear what you're saying\n[01:23.192] When I was a child I had a fever\n[01:30.680] My hands felt just like two balloons\n[01:38.474] Now I've got that feeling once again\n[01:42.889] I can't explain you would not understand\n[01:47.820] This is not how I am\n[01:53.636] I have become comfortably numb\n[02:35.192] I have become comfortably numb\n[02:46.648] Okay\n[02:47.225] (Okay okay okay)\n[02:49.369] Just a little pinprick\n[02:52.872] There'll be no more\n[02:56.932] But you may feel a little sick\n[03:01.045] Can you stand up?\n[03:02.131] Stand up stand up\n[03:04.171] I do believe it's working good\n[03:08.185] That'll keep you going through the show\n[03:12.708] Come on it's time to go\n[03:17.108] There is no pain you are receding\n[03:24.631] A distant ship smoke on the horizon\n[03:31.990] You are only coming through in waves\n[03:39.044] Your lips move but I can't hear what you're saying\n[03:46.619] When I was a child I caught a fleeting glimpse\n[03:54.852] Out of the corner of my eye\n[04:02.421] I turned to look but it was gone\n[04:06.317] I cannot put my finger on it now\n[04:11.007] The child is grown the dream is gone\n[04:17.119] I have become comfortably numb",
