        "fullLyrics": "[00:30.960] Adventure seeker \n[00:33.180] On an empty street \n[00:35.790] Just an alley creeper \n[00:38.310] Light on his feet \n[00:41.040] A young fighter screaming \n[00:43.530] With no time for doubt \n[00:46.140] With the pain and anger \n[00:48.840] Can't see a way out \n[00:50.070] It ain't much I'm asking \n[00:53.790] I heard him say \n[00:56.640] Gotta find me a future \n[00:59.070] Move out of my way \n[01:01.770] I want it all I want it all \n[01:06.930] I want it all and I want it now \n[01:12.030] I want it all I want it all \n[01:17.280] I want it all and I want it now \n[01:22.470] Listen all you people \n[01:25.020] Come gather round \n[01:27.690] I gotta get me a game plan \n[01:30.420] Gonna shake you to the ground \n[01:33.690] Just give me what I know is mine \n[01:38.700] People do you hear me \n[01:40.800] Just give me the sign \n[01:43.260] It ain't much I'm asking \n[01:46.200] If you want the truth \n[01:48.690] Here's to the future \n[01:51.420] For the dreams of youth \n[01:53.910] I want it all I want it all \n[01:59.160] I want it all and I want it now \n[02:04.320] I want it all I want it all \n[02:09.509] I want it all and I want it now \n[02:18.630] I'm a man with a one track mind \n[02:20.850] So much to do in one life time \n[02:22.920] People do you hear me \n[02:23.850] Not a man for compromise and wheres \n[02:26.280] And whys and living lies \n[02:28.170] So I'm living it all \n[02:29.340] Yes I'm living it all \n[02:30.810] And I'm giving it all \n[02:32.130] And I'm giving it all \n[03:36.900] It ain't much I'm asking \n[03:38.730] If you want the truth \n[03:41.970] Here's to the future \n[03:44.700] Hear the cry of youth \n[03:47.250] I want it all I want it all \n[03:52.350] I want it all and I want it now \n[03:57.570] I want it all I want it all \n[04:02.730] I want it all and I want it now \n[04:15.690] I want it now \n[04:16.230] I want it I want it now",
