        "chorusTitle": "Verse",
        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:45.449] Oceans apart day after day\n[00:51.386] And I slowly go insane\n[00:56.073] I hear your voice on the line\n[01:02.198] But it doesn't stop the pain\n[01:06.767] If I see you next to never\n[01:12.095] How can we say forever\n[01:17.219] Wherever you go\n[01:19.867] Whatever you do\n[01:22.469] I will be right here\n[01:25.093] Waiting for you\n[01:27.843] Whatever it takes\n[01:30.593] Or how my heart breaks\n[01:32.905] I will be right here\n[01:35.905] Waiting for you\n[01:44.585] I took for granted all the times\n[01:50.584] That I thought would last somehow\n[01:55.334] I hear the laughter\n[01:57.958] I taste the tears\n[02:01.458] But I can't get near you now\n[02:06.020] Oh can't you see it baby\n[02:11.457] You've got me going crazy\n[02:16.519] Wherever you go\n[02:19.012] Whatever you do\n[02:21.574] I will be right here\n[02:24.442] Waiting for you\n[02:27.192] Whatever it takes\n[02:29.754] Or how my heart breaks\n[02:32.191] I will be right here\n[02:35.175] Waiting for you\n[02:38.690] I wonder how we can survive\n[02:44.025] This romance\n[02:49.587] But in the end if I'm with you\n[02:53.649] I'll take the chance\n[03:21.481] Oh can't you see it baby\n[03:26.786] You've got me going crazy\n[03:31.724] Wherever you go\n[03:34.411] Whatever you do\n[03:36.806] I will be right here\n[03:39.723] Waiting for you\n[03:42.538] Whatever it takes\n[03:45.163] Or how my heart breaks\n[03:47.757] I will be right here\n[03:50.534] Waiting for you\n[04:02.136] Waiting for you",
