        "fullLyrics": "[00:08.905] Come and hold my hand\n[00:12.895] I wanna contact the living\n[00:18.439] Not sure I understand\n[00:23.342] This role I've been given\n[00:28.342] I sit and talk to god\n[00:32.534] And he just laughs at my plans\n[00:37.866] My head speaks language\n[00:42.902] I don't understand\n[00:48.123] I just want to feel real love\n[00:52.388] Feel the home that I live in\n[00:57.627] Cause I got too much life\n[01:00.282] Running through my veins\n[01:02.641] Going to waste\n[01:07.576] I don't want to die\n[01:11.504] But I ain't keen on living either\n[01:17.213] Before I fall in love\n[01:21.734] I'm preparing to leave her\n[01:27.259] Scare myself to death\n[01:31.801] That's why I keep on running\n[01:36.814] Before I've arrived\n[01:41.428] I can see myself coming\n[01:46.817] I just want to feel real love\n[01:51.170] Feel the home that I live in\n[01:56.458] Cause I got too much life\n[01:59.057] Running through my veins\n[02:01.645] Going to waste\n[02:06.096] And I need to feel real love\n[02:10.852] And a life ever after\n[02:15.947] I can not give it up\n[02:35.764] I just want to feel real love\n[02:40.162] Feel the home that I live in\n[02:45.505] I got too much life\n[02:48.035] Running through my veins\n[02:50.139] To go to waste\n[02:55.381] I just want to feel real love\n[02:59.654] In a life ever after\n[03:04.555] There's a hole in my soul\n[03:07.080] You can see it in my face\n[03:09.501] It's a real big place\n[03:19.786] Come and hold my hand\n[03:23.842] I want to contact the living\n[03:29.410] Not sure I understand\n[03:34.404] This role I've been given",
