        "fullLyrics": "[00:23.923] Hell is gone and heaven's here\n[00:26.254] There's nothing left for you to fear\n[00:27.786] Shake your a** come over here\n[00:29.126] Now scream\n[00:30.943] I'm a burning effigy\n[00:32.858] Of everything I used to be\n[00:34.741] You're my rock of empathy  my dear\n[00:38.064] So come on let me entertain you\n[00:46.255] Let me entertain you\n[00:53.991] Life's too short for you to die\n[00:55.738] So grab yourself an alibi\n[00:57.552] Heaven knows your mother lied\n[00:59.497] Mon cher\n[01:01.672] Separate your right from wrongs\n[01:03.457] Come and sing a different song\n[01:05.061] The kettle's on so don't be long\n[01:07.117] Mon cher\n[01:08.878] So come on let me entertain you\n[01:17.052] Let me entertain you\n[01:24.706] Look me up in the yellow pages\n[01:26.269] I will be your rock of ages\n[01:28.082] Your see through fads and your crazy phases yeah\n[01:32.365] Little Bo Peep has lost his sheep\n[01:34.303] He popped a pill and fell asleep\n[01:35.926] The dew is wet but the grass is sweet my dear\n[01:39.735] Your mind gets burned\n[01:41.833] With the habits you've learned\n[01:43.505] But we're the generation that's got to be heard\n[01:47.607] You're tired of your teachers and your school's a drag\n[01:51.430] You're not going to end up like your mum and dad\n[01:54.930] So come on let me entertain you\n[02:02.931] Let me entertain you\n[02:10.697] Let me entertain you\n[02:18.083] He may be good he may be outta sight\n[02:22.019] But he can't be here so come around tonight\n[02:26.068] Here is the place where the feeling grows\n[02:29.701] You gotta get high before you get taste the lows\n[02:33.194] So come on\n[02:49.323] Let me entertain you\n[02:56.771] Let me entertain you\n[03:04.150] So come on let me entertain you\n[03:12.050] Let me entertain you\n[03:19.872] Come on come on come on come on\n[03:21.689] Come on come on come on come on\n[03:23.557] Come on come on come on come on",
