        "fullLyrics": "[00:18.277] In a time where the sun descends alone\n[00:25.158] I ran a long long way from home\n[00:29.810] To find a heart that's made of stone\n[00:36.395] I will try  I just need a little time\n[00:43.595] To get your face right out of my mind\n[00:48.055] To see the world through different eyes\n[00:55.791] Every time I see you oh I try to hide away\n[00:59.294] But when we meet it seems I can't let go\n[01:04.860] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[01:12.846] Tell me why\n[01:15.263] When I scream there's no reply\n[01:19.800] When I reach out there's nothing to find\n[01:24.554] When I sleep I break down and cry\n[01:29.114] Cry  yeah\n[01:31.639] Every time I see you oh I try to hide away\n[01:36.784] But when we meet it seems I can't let go\n[01:41.364] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[01:48.799] Fading like a rose\n[01:53.484] Fading like a rose\n[01:58.032] Beaten by the storm\n[02:02.700] Talking to myself\n[02:04.664] Getting washed by the rain\n[02:06.639] It's such a cold cold town\n[02:10.479] Oh  it's a such cold town\n[02:27.343] Every time I see you oh I try to hide away\n[02:31.553] But when we meet it seems I can't let go\n[02:36.283] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[02:43.043] Every time I see you oh I try to hide away\n[02:47.423] But when we meet it seems I can't let go\n[02:52.143] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[02:57.078] Every time I see you oh I try to hide away\n[03:01.173] But when we meet it seems I can't let go\n[03:05.737] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[03:12.022] Oh\n[03:22.115] Every time you leave the room I feel I'm fading like a flower\n[03:27.162] Every time I see you I'm fading like a rose",
