        "fullLyrics": "[00:11.191] Wrap me in a bolt of lightning\n[00:12.681] Send me on my way still smiling\n[00:14.821] Maybe that's the way I should go\n[00:17.521] Straight into the mouth of the unknown\n[00:19.771] I left the spare key on the table\n[00:22.471] Never really thought I'd be able to say\n[00:26.101] I merely visit on the weekends\n[00:27.601] I lost my whole life and a dear friend\n[00:30.411] I've said it so many times\n[00:33.591] I would change my ways\n[00:37.581] No  nevermind\n[00:38.831] God knows I've tried\n[00:42.891] Call me a sinner  call me a saint\n[00:48.471] Tell me it's over I'll still love you the same\n[00:53.921] Call me your favorite  call me the worst\n[00:58.471] Tell me it's over I don't wan't you to hurt\n[01:03.651] It's all that I can say\n[01:07.391] So  I'll be on my way\n[01:12.201] I finally put it all together\n[01:24.731] But nothing really lasts forever\n[01:26.801] I had to make a choice that was not mine\n[01:30.321] I had to say goodbye for the last time\n[01:32.631] I kept my whole life in suitcase\n[01:34.691] Never really stayed in one place\n[01:37.001] Maybe that's the way it should be\n[01:39.811] You know I've led my life like a gypsy\n[01:42.551] I've said it so many times\n[01:45.801] I would change my ways\n[01:49.981] No  nevermind\n[01:51.291] God knows I've tried\n[01:55.111] Call me a sinner  call me a saint\n[02:00.761] Tell me it's over I'll still love you the same\n[02:06.141] Call me your favorite  call me the worst\n[02:11.011] Tell me it's over I don't wan't you to hurt\n[02:16.251] It's all that I can say\n[02:19.561] So  I'll be on my way\n[02:24.561] I'll always keep you inside\n[02:29.671] You healed my heart and my life\n[02:32.611] And you know I try\n[02:38.451] Call me a sinner  call me a saint\n[02:43.521] Tell me it's over I'll still love you the same\n[02:48.511] Call me your favorite  call me the worst\n[02:53.441] Tell me it's over I don't wan't you to hurt\n[02:58.431] It's all that I can say\n[03:01.681] So  I'll be on my way\n[03:07.001] So  I'll be on my way\n[03:11.691] So  I'll be on my way\n[03:17.031] End",
