        "fullLyrics": "[00:00.717] Get up get up\n[00:03.940] Get up get up\n[00:07.373] Get up get up\n[00:10.629] Get up get up get up get up\n[00:13.315] Get up get up\n[00:15.753] I know you're clinging to the light of day\n[00:21.282] To tell you everythings a-okay\n[00:26.957] And medication don't do much\n[00:32.279] Yeah it just numbs the brain\n[00:38.229] Guess you might say I'm a little intense\n[00:43.704] I'm on the bright side of being hell bent\n[00:48.129] So take it from me you're not the only one\n[00:53.470] Who can't see straight can't see straight\n[01:00.486] If you were ever in doubt\n[01:03.624] Don't sell yourself short you might be bulletproof\n[01:06.561] Hard to move mountains when you're paralyzed\n[01:09.350] But you gotta try\n[01:11.577] And I'm calling out\n[01:13.363] Get up get up\n[01:14.514] Get a move on\n[01:16.426] Get up get up\n[01:17.681] What's taking so long\n[01:19.624] Get up get up\n[01:20.870] Get a move on\n[01:22.901] Stop stalling I'm calling out\n[01:26.150] Get up get up\n[01:27.267] Get a move on\n[01:29.187] Get up get up\n[01:30.484] Ain't nothing wrong\n[01:32.791] 'Cause I believe you can be whatever\n[01:39.197] And I agree you can do much better trust me\n[01:51.152] Everybody wants to sing that song\n[01:56.393] Some Marvin Gaye what's going on\n[02:02.092] Ain't nothing normal when it comes to you and me\n[02:06.947] I'd rather twist myself in knots than watch you give up on your dreams\n[02:13.312] If you were ever in doubt\n[02:16.403] Don't sell yourself short you might be bulletproof\n[02:19.288] Hard to move mountains when you're paralyzed\n[02:22.062] But you gotta try\n[02:24.544] So I'm calling out\n[02:26.181] Get up get up\n[02:27.285] Get a move on\n[02:29.191] Get up get up\n[02:30.437] What's taking so long\n[02:32.394] Get up get up\n[02:33.668] Get a move on\n[02:35.606] Stop stalling I'm calling out\n[02:38.893] Get up get up\n[02:40.008] Get a move on\n[02:42.027] Get up get up\n[02:43.240] Ain't nothing wrong\n[02:45.644] 'Cause I believe you can be whatever\n[02:52.048] And I agree you can do much better trust me\n[03:00.281] Yeah I don't know why I never talked about it\n[03:03.433] I guess that's probably part of the problem\n[03:06.529] Yeah sometimes you're wrong sometimes you're right\n[03:10.178] Just gotta keep moving\n[03:12.481] Yeah I'm just gonna keep moving\n[03:16.505] Today tomorrow and the next\n[03:19.583] Get up get up\n[03:20.674] Get a move on\n[03:22.542] Get up get up\n[03:23.825] What's taking so long\n[03:25.754] Get up get up\n[03:27.014] Get a move on\n[03:29.019] Stop stalling I'm calling out\n[03:32.269] Get up get up\n[03:33.399] Get a move on\n[03:35.381] Get up get up\n[03:36.621] Ain't nothing wrong\n[03:38.960] 'Cause I believe you can be whatever\n[03:45.335] And I agree you can do much better trust me\n[03:51.461] Get up get up\n[03:54.692] Get up get up\n[03:56.126] Get up get up\n[03:57.363] Get up get up",
