        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:18.901] You'll remember me when the west wind moves\n[00:24.081] Upon the fields of barley\n[00:27.771] You'll forget the sun in his jealous sky\n[00:32.441] As we walk in fields of gold\n[00:44.001] So she took her love\n[00:46.251] For to gaze awhile\n[00:49.121] Upon the fields of barley\n[00:53.111] In his arms she fell as her hair came down\n[00:57.851] Among the fields of gold\n[01:02.411] Will you stay with me  will you be my love\n[01:06.771] Among the fields of barley\n[01:11.591] We'll forget the sun in his jealous sky\n[01:16.201] As we lie in fields of gold\n[01:27.881] See the west wind move like a lover so\n[01:33.001] Upon the fields of barley\n[01:36.871] Feel her body rise when you kiss her mouth\n[01:41.551] Among the fields of gold\n[01:47.921] I never made promises lightly\n[01:51.791] And there have been some that I've broken\n[01:56.481] But I swear in the days still left\n[02:00.161] We'll walk in fields of gold\n[02:04.711] We'll walk in fields of gold\n[02:30.215] Many years have passed since those summer days\n[02:34.765] Among the fields of barley\n[02:39.325] See the children run as the sun goes down\n[02:43.875] Among the fields of gold\n[02:48.495] You'll remember me when the west wind moves\n[02:53.745] Upon the fields of barley\n[02:57.735] You can tell the sun in his jealous sky\n[03:02.355] When we walked in fields of gold\n[03:07.045] When we walked in fields of gold",
