        "fullLyrics": "[00:17.211] I guess now it's time\n[00:21.571] For me to give up\n[00:24.631] I fill it's time\n[00:28.241] Got a picture of you beside me\n[00:31.241] Got your lipstick mark\n[00:32.931] Still on your coffee cup\n[00:36.491] Oh yeah\n[00:40.481] Got a fist of pure emotion\n[00:43.231] Got a head of shattered dreams\n[00:46.401] Gotta leave it\n[00:47.841] Gotta leave it all behind now\n[00:52.731] Whatever I said\n[00:54.281] Whatever I did I didn't mean it\n[00:56.901] I just want you back for good\n[00:59.371] Want you back\n[01:00.551] Want you back\n[01:02.301] Want you back for good\n[01:04.861] Whenever I'm wrong just tell me the song\n[01:07.541] And I'll sing it\n[01:08.981] You'll be right and understand\n[01:11.731] Want you back\n[01:12.911] Want you back\n[01:13.911] I want you back for good\n[01:17.981] Unaware but underlined\n[01:21.991] I figured out this story\n[01:25.731] It wasn't good\n[01:28.721] But in the corner of my mind\n[01:34.021] I celebrated glory\n[01:37.711] But that was not to be\n[01:41.021] In the twist of separation\n[01:43.951] You excelled at being free\n[01:47.071] Can't you find\n[01:48.071] A little room inside for me\n[01:53.441] Whatever I said\n[01:55.061] Whatever I did I didn't mean it\n[01:57.611] I just want you back for good\n[02:00.131] Want you back\n[02:01.451] Want you back\n[02:02.441] Say you want back for good\n[02:05.561] Whenever I'm wrong just tell me the song\n[02:08.311] And I'll sing it\n[02:09.741] You'll be right and understand\n[02:12.421] Want you back\n[02:13.051] Want you back\n[02:14.801] I want you back for good\n[02:19.101] And we'll be together\n[02:25.091] This time is forever\n[02:31.331] We'll be fighting and forever we will be\n[02:35.521] So complete in our love\n[02:38.631] We will never be uncovered again\n[02:48.431] Whatever I said\n[02:50.111] Whatever I did I didn't mean it\n[02:52.861] I just want you back for good\n[02:55.921] Want you back\n[02:56.671] Want you back\n[02:58.161] Want you back for good\n[03:00.721] Whenever I'm wrong just tell me the song\n[03:03.411] And I'll sing it\n[03:04.841] You'll be right and understand\n[03:07.961] Want you back\n[03:08.531] Want you back\n[03:09.711] Say you want back for good\n[03:13.261] Whatever I said\n[03:14.081] Whatever I did I didn't mean it\n[03:17.571] I just want you back for good\n[03:19.621] Want you back\n[03:20.451] Want you back\n[03:21.321] I want you back for good\n[03:25.061] Whenever I'm wrong just tell me the song\n[03:27.491] And I'll sing it\n[03:28.621] You'll be right and understand\n[03:31.051] Want you back\n[03:31.731] Want you back\n[03:33.881] Say you want back for good\n[03:39.321] Oh yeah\n[03:44.311] I guess now it 's time\n[03:47.991] You came back for good",
