        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:11.568] Betty I won't make assumptions about\n[00:14.460] Why you switched your homeroom\n[00:16.226] But I think it's cause of me\n[00:21.381] Betty one time I was riding on my skateboard\n[00:24.958] When I passed your house\n[00:26.672] It's like I couldn't breathe\n[00:31.100] You heard the rumors from Inez\n[00:33.500] You can't believe a word she says\n[00:36.228] Most times but this time it was true\n[00:40.520] The worst thing that I ever did\n[00:45.503] Was what I did to you\n[00:52.335] But if I just showed up at your party\n[00:55.015] Would you have me\n[00:56.231] Would you want me\n[00:57.588] Would you tell me to go fuck myself\n[01:00.268] Or lead me to the garden\n[01:02.428] In the garden would you trust me\n[01:05.084] If I told you it was just a summer thing\n[01:08.796] I'm only seventeen\n[01:10.420] I don't know anything\n[01:12.372] But I know I miss you\n[01:23.839] Betty I know where it all went wrong your favorite song\n[01:27.879] Was playing from the far side of the gym\n[01:33.599] I was nowhere to be found\n[01:35.895] I hate the crowds\n[01:37.167] You know that\n[01:38.823] Plus I saw you dance with him\n[01:43.536] You heard the rumors from Inez\n[01:46.000] You can't believe a word she says\n[01:48.598] Most times but this time it was true\n[01:53.021] The worst thing that I ever did\n[01:57.863] Was what I did to you\n[02:04.835] But if I just showed up at your party\n[02:07.411] Would you have me\n[02:08.707] Would you want me\n[02:09.971] Would you tell me to go fuck myself\n[02:12.843] Or lead me to the garden\n[02:14.891] In the garden would you trust me\n[02:17.515] If I told you it was just a summer thing\n[02:21.139] I'm only seventeen\n[02:22.851] I don't know anything\n[02:24.555] But I know I miss you\n[02:36.092] I was walking home on broken cobblestones\n[02:39.759] Just thinking of you\n[02:41.462] When she pulled up\n[02:42.526] Like a figment of my worst intentions\n[02:45.556] She said James get in let's drive\n[02:48.820] Those days turned into nights\n[02:51.148] Slept next to her but\n[02:53.368] I dreamt of you all summer long\n[03:13.990] Betty I'm here on your doorstep\n[03:16.389] And I planned it out for weeks now\n[03:18.823] But it's finally sinking in\n[03:23.875] Betty right now is the last time\n[03:26.283] I can dream about what happens when you see my face again\n[03:32.819] The only thing I wanna do\n[03:37.852] Is make it up to you\n[03:45.164] So I showed up at your party\n[03:55.108] Yeah I showed up at your party\n[04:04.820] Yeah I showed up at your party\n[04:07.524] Will you have me\n[04:08.620] Will you love me\n[04:10.084] Will you kiss me on the porch in front of all your stupid friends\n[04:14.844] If you kiss me\n[04:16.164] Will it be just like I dreamed it\n[04:18.900] Will it patch your broken wings\n[04:21.044] I'm only seventeen\n[04:22.868] I don't know anything\n[04:24.660] But I know I miss you\n[04:29.730] Standing in your cardigan\n[04:34.763] Kissing in my car again\n[04:38.441] Stopped at a streetlight\n[04:39.952] You know I miss you",
