        "fullLyrics": "[00:13.704] I see your face in my mind as I drive away\n[00:19.976] 'Cause none of us thought it was gonna end that way\n[00:26.665] People are people and sometimes we change our minds\n[00:32.609] But it's killing me to see you go after all this time\n[00:52.594] Music starts playing like the end of a sad movie\n[00:58.886] It's the kind of ending you don't really wanna see\n[01:05.119] 'Cause it's tragedy and it'll only bring you down\n[01:11.694] Now I don't know what to be without you around\n[01:18.886] And we know it's never simple never easy\n[01:21.962] Never a clean break no one here to save me\n[01:24.898] You're the only thing I know like the back of my hand\n[01:30.292] And I can't breathe without you but I have to\n[01:38.420] Breathe without you but I have to\n[01:51.063] Never wanted this never wanna see you hurt\n[01:57.457] Every little bump in the road I tried to swerve\n[02:03.738] But people are people and sometimes it doesn't work out\n[02:10.351] Nothing we say is gonna save us from the fall out\n[02:17.199] And we know it's never simple never easy\n[02:20.480] Never a clean break no one here to save me\n[02:23.366] You're the only thing I know like the back of my hand\n[02:28.694] And I can't breathe without you but I have to\n[02:36.762] Breathe without you but I have to\n[02:55.720] It's 2 A.M feeling like I just lost a friend\n[03:01.110] Hope you know it's not easy easy for me\n[03:08.383] It's 2 A.M feeling like I just lost a friend\n[03:14.110] Hope you know this ain't easy easy for me\n[03:22.357] And we know it's never simple never easy\n[03:25.349] Never a clean break no one here to save me oh-oh\n[03:33.918] I can't breathe without you but I have to\n[03:41.639] Breathe without you but I have to\n[03:48.071] Breathe without you but I have to\n[04:00.813] I'm sorry I'm sorry\n[04:03.526] Mmm\n[04:04.294] I'm sorry\n[04:05.072] Yeah yeah\n[04:06.033] I'm sorry\n[04:07.457] I'm sorry I'm sorry\n[04:10.603] I'm sorry",
