        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:13.708] There I was again tonight forcing laughter faking smiles\n[00:19.497] Same old tired lonely place\n[00:25.615] Walls of insincerity\n[00:28.129] Shifting eyes and vacancy vanished when I saw your face\n[00:34.642] All I can say is it was enchanting to meet you\n[00:48.796] Your eyes whispered have we met\n[00:51.734] Across the room your silhouette starts to make its way to me\n[01:00.363] The playful conversation starts\n[01:03.356] Counter all your quick remarks like passing notes in secrecy\n[01:11.346] And it was enchanting to meet you\n[01:21.315] All I can say is I was enchanted to meet you\n[01:36.405] This night is sparkling don't you let it go\n[01:42.246] I'm wonderstruck blushing all the way home\n[01:48.108] I'll spend forever wondering if you knew\n[01:53.913] I was enchanted to meet you\n[02:04.892] The lingering question kept me up\n[02:07.903] 2 am who do you love\n[02:10.701] I wonder till I'm wide awake\n[02:16.502] And now I'm pacing back and forth wishing you were at my door\n[02:22.476] I'd open up and you would say \"Hey\"\n[02:28.384] It was enchanting to meet you\n[02:37.860] All I know is I was enchanted to meet you\n[02:52.493] This night is sparkling don't you let it go\n[02:58.266] I'm wonderstruck blushing all the way home\n[03:04.053] I'll spend forever wondering if you knew\n[03:15.798] This night is flawless don't you let it go\n[03:21.808] I'm wonderstruck dancing around all alone\n[03:27.577] I'll spend forever wondering if you knew\n[03:33.299] I was enchanted to meet you\n[03:59.033] This is me praying that this was the very first page\n[04:05.516] Not where the story line ends\n[04:08.333] My thoughts will echo your name until I see you again\n[04:14.252] These are the words I held back as I was leaving too soon\n[04:20.063] I was enchanted to meet you\n[04:26.084] Please don't be in love with someone else\n[04:31.405] Please don't have somebody waiting on you\n[04:37.087] Please don't be in love with someone else\n[04:43.113] Please don't have somebody waiting on you\n[04:49.634] This night is sparkling don't you let it go\n[04:55.515] I'm wonderstruck blushing all the way home\n[05:01.237] I'll spend forever wondering if you knew\n[05:12.992] This night is flawless don't you let it go\n[05:18.876] I'm wonderstruck dancing around all alone\n[05:24.649] I'll spend forever wondering if you knew\n[05:30.376] I was enchanted to meet you\n[05:36.381] Please don't be in love with someone else\n[05:41.726] Please don't have somebody waiting on you",
