        "fullLyrics": "[00:10.771] You take a deep breath and you walk through the doors\n[00:14.440] It's the morning of your very first day\n[00:20.168] You say hi to your friends who ain't seen in a while\n[00:24.376] Try and stay out of everybody's way\n[00:30.557] It's your freshman year and you're gonna be here\n[00:34.525] For the next four years in this town\n[00:39.688] Hoping one of those senior boys will wink at you and say\n[00:45.023] You know I haven't seen you around  before\n[00:52.101] 'Cause when you're fifteen\n[00:55.808] Somebody tells you they love you\n[00:59.259] You're gonna believe them\n[01:01.994] And when you're fifteen feeling like\n[01:07.008] There's nothing to figure out  but\n[01:13.386] Count to ten  take it in\n[01:15.813] This is life before you know\n[01:18.432] Who you're gonna be\n[01:24.294] Fifteen\n[01:36.080] You sit in a class next to a redhead Abigail\n[01:40.208] And soon enough you're best friends\n[01:45.723] Laughing at the others girls\n[01:47.787] Who think they're so cool\n[01:49.808] We'll be out of here as soon as we can\n[01:55.466] And then you're on you're very first date\n[01:58.688] And he's got a car and you're feeling like flying\n[02:05.477] And you're mamma's waiting up and you're thinking he's the one\n[02:09.813] And you're dancing 'round your room when the night ends\n[02:14.895] When the night ends\n[02:17.376] 'Cause when you're fifteen\n[02:21.086] Somebody tells you they love you\n[02:24.383] You're gonna believe them\n[02:27.364] And when you're fifteen and your first kiss\n[02:33.007] Makes you head spin 'round but\n[02:38.725] In your life you'll do things greater\n[02:41.860] Than dating the boy on the football team\n[02:47.413] But I didn't know it at fifteen\n[03:01.994] When all you wanted\n[03:04.383] Was to be wanted\n[03:06.836] Wish you could go back\n[03:08.362] And tell yourself what you know now\n[03:16.580] Back then I swore I was gonna\n[03:18.832] Marry him someday\n[03:20.558] But I realized some bigger dreams of mine\n[03:26.046] And Abigail gave everything she had to a boy\n[03:31.961] Who changed his mind\n[03:35.002] And we both cried\n[03:37.684] 'Cause when you're fifteen \n[03:41.362] Somebody tells you they love you\n[03:44.791] You're gonna believe them\n[03:47.667] And when you're fifteen \n[03:50.770] Don't forget to look before you fall\n[03:59.036] I've found time can heal most anything\n[04:02.728] And you just might find who you're supposed to be\n[04:07.901] I didn't know who I was supposed to be\n[04:14.712] At fifteen\n[04:21.991] Lalalalalalala\n[04:34.631] Your very first day\n[04:39.303] Take a deep breath girl\n[04:42.002] Take a deep breath as you walk through the doors",
