        "fullLyrics": "[00:17.326] The way you move is like a full on rainstorm\n[00:21.444] And I'm a house of cards\n[00:24.660] You're the kind of reckless\n[00:26.804] That should send me running\n[00:29.061] But I kinda know that I won't get far\n[00:33.969] And you stood there in front of me\n[00:37.177] Just close enough to touch\n[00:42.490] Close enough to hope you couldn't see\n[00:46.441] What I was thinking of\n[00:48.873] Drop everything now\n[00:51.188] Meet me in the pouring rain\n[00:54.523] Kiss me on the sidewalk\n[00:56.570] Take away the pain\n[00:58.520] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[01:06.103] Get me with those green eyes baby as the lights go down\n[01:10.888] Give me something that'll haunt me when you're not around\n[01:15.235] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[01:32.579] My mind forgets to remind me\n[01:36.839] You're a bad idea\n[01:40.898] You touch me once and it's really something\n[01:44.363] You find I'm even better than you imagined I would be\n[01:49.233] I'm on my guard for the rest of the world\n[01:52.390] But with you I know it's no good\n[01:57.583] And I could wait patiently but I really wish you would\n[02:04.149] Drop everything now\n[02:06.479] Meet me in the pouring rain\n[02:09.810] Kiss me on the sidewalk\n[02:11.910] Take away the pain\n[02:13.827] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[02:21.374] Get me with those green eyes baby as the lights go down\n[02:26.112] Give me something that'll haunt me when you're not around\n[02:30.317] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[02:47.316] I run my fingers through your hair and watch the lights go wild\n[02:55.664] Just keep on keeping your eyes on me\n[02:59.379] It's just wrong enough to make it feel right\n[03:04.037] And lead me up the staircase\n[03:07.082] Won't you whisper soft and slow\n[03:12.389] I'm captivated by you baby like a firework show\n[03:19.341] Drop everything now\n[03:21.797] Meet me in the pouring rain\n[03:25.042] Kiss me on the sidewalk\n[03:27.208] Take away the pain\n[03:28.867] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[03:36.438] Get me with those green eyes baby as the lights go down\n[03:41.467] Give me something that'll haunt me when you're not around\n[03:45.717] 'Cause I see sparks fly whenever you smile\n[03:58.016] And the sparks fly\n[04:01.642] Oh baby smile\n[04:06.255] And the sparks fly",
