        "fullLyrics": "[00:04.566] I am not the kind of girl\n[00:07.643] Who should be rudely barging in on a white veil occasion\n[00:12.257] But you are not the kind of boy\n[00:15.761] Who should be marrying the wrong girl\n[00:20.514] I sneak in and see your friends\n[00:23.955] And her snotty little family all dressed in pastel\n[00:28.194] And she is yelling at a bridesmaid\n[00:32.054] Somewhere back inside a room\n[00:33.848] Wearing a gown shaped like a pastry\n[00:36.663] This is surely not what you thought it would be\n[00:44.756] I lose myself in a daydream\n[00:51.111] Where I stand and say\n[00:53.157] Don't say yes\n[00:54.656] Run away now\n[00:56.581] I'll meet you when you're out of the church at the back door\n[01:01.246] Don't wait or say a single vow\n[01:04.611] You need to hear me out\n[01:06.520] And they said speak now\n[01:16.987] Fond gestures are exchanged\n[01:20.595] And the organ starts to play\n[01:22.231] A song that sounds like a death March\n[01:24.874] And I am hiding in the curtains\n[01:28.397] It seems that I was uninvited by your lovely bride-to-be\n[01:32.976] She floats down the aisle like a pageant queen\n[01:41.022] But I know you wish it was me\n[01:47.062] You wish it was me\n[01:48.477] Don't you\n[01:49.639] Don't say yes\n[01:51.122] Run away now\n[01:53.125] I'll meet you when you're out of the church at the back door\n[01:57.779] Don't wait or say a single vow\n[02:01.051] You need to hear me out\n[02:02.893] And they said speak now\n[02:05.757] Don't say yes\n[02:07.247] Run away now\n[02:09.224] I'll meet you when you're out of the church at the back door\n[02:13.960] Don't wait or say a single vow\n[02:17.112] Your time is running out\n[02:18.975] And they said speak now\n[02:23.927] Oh la la\n[02:27.479] Oh oh\n[02:32.522] Say a single vow\n[02:37.781] I hear the preacher say\n[02:39.572] Speak now or forever hold your peace\n[02:45.761] There's the silence there's my last chance\n[02:47.868] I stand up with shaky hands all eyes on me\n[02:53.794] Horrified looks from everyone in the room\n[02:57.342] But I'm only looking at you\n[03:02.070] I am not the kind of girl\n[03:05.230] Who should be rudely barging in on a white veil occasion\n[03:09.794] But you are not the kind of boy\n[03:13.183] Who should be marrying the wrong girl\n[03:18.204] So don't say yes\n[03:19.919] Run away now\n[03:21.869] I'll meet you when you're out of the church at the back door\n[03:26.587] Don't wait or say a single vow\n[03:29.834] You need to hear me out\n[03:31.916] And they said\n[03:32.568] Speak now\n[03:34.573] And you say\n[03:36.104] Let's run away now\n[03:37.912] I'll meet you when I'm out of my tux at the back door\n[03:42.649] Baby I didn't say my vows\n[03:45.997] So glad you were around\n[03:47.975] When they said\n[03:48.731] Speak now",
