        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:17.217] I'm five years old\n[00:19.185] It's getting cold\n[00:21.063] I've got my big coat on\n[00:24.862] I hear your laugh\n[00:26.726] And look up smiling at you\n[00:29.852] I run and run\n[00:32.275] Past the pumpkin patch\n[00:34.476] And the tractor rides\n[00:36.076] Look now the sky is gold\n[00:40.045] I hug your legs and fall asleep\n[00:45.385] On the way home\n[00:48.278] I don't know why all the trees change in the fall\n[00:55.725] I know you're not scared of anything at all\n[01:02.790] Don't know if snow white's house is near or far away\n[01:08.466] But I know I had the best day\n[01:11.581] With you today\n[01:22.002] I'm thirteen now\n[01:23.837] And don't know how my friends\n[01:26.664] Could be so mean\n[01:29.441] I come home crying and you hold me tight and grab the keys\n[01:36.918] And we drive and drive\n[01:39.095] Until we've found a town\n[01:41.777] Far enough away\n[01:44.537] And we talk and window shop\n[01:47.405] Until I've forgotten all their names\n[01:52.861] I don't know who I'm gonna talk to\n[01:56.797] Now at school\n[02:00.467] I know I'm laughing on the car ride home with you\n[02:07.552] Don't know how long it's gonna take to feel okay\n[02:13.452] But I know I had the best day\n[02:16.197] With you today\n[02:22.989] I have an excellent father\n[02:26.524] His strength is making me stronger\n[02:30.278] God smiles on my little brother\n[02:33.839] Inside and out\n[02:35.302] He's better than I am\n[02:37.782] I grew up in a pretty house\n[02:41.895] And I had space to run\n[02:45.054] And I had the best days with you\n[02:53.352] There is a video\n[02:56.112] I found from back when I was three\n[03:00.721] You set up a paint set in the kitchen\n[03:05.177] And you're talking to me\n[03:08.277] It's the age of princesses and pirate ships\n[03:13.340] And the seven dwarfs\n[03:15.966] Daddy's smart\n[03:17.306] And you're the prettiest lady in the whole wide world\n[03:24.338] Now I know why all the trees change in the fall\n[03:31.317] I know you were on my side\n[03:34.722] Even when I was wrong\n[03:37.866] And I love you for giving me your eyes\n[03:42.585] Staying back and watching me shine\n[03:46.368] And I didn't know if you knew\n[03:49.193] So I'm taking this chance to say\n[03:52.463] That I had the best day\n[03:55.014] With you today",
