        "fullLyrics": "[00:05.716] Yesterday\n[00:08.772] All my troubles seemed so far away\n[00:13.674] Now it looks as though they're here to stay\n[00:17.468] Oh I believe in yesterday\n[00:22.855] Suddenly\n[00:26.000] I'm not half the man I used to be\n[00:30.874] There's a shadow hanging over me\n[00:34.884] Oh yesterday came suddenly\n[00:40.155] Why she had to go I don't know\n[00:45.797] She wouldn't say\n[00:49.991] I said something wrong\n[00:54.442] Now I long for yesterday\n[00:59.995] Yesterday\n[01:03.030] Love was such an easy game to play\n[01:08.155] Now I need a place to hide away\n[01:11.877] Oh I believe in yesterday\n[01:17.757] Why she had to go I don't know\n[01:23.353] She wouldn't say\n[01:27.607] I said something wrong\n[01:31.919] Now I long for yesterday\n[01:37.769] Yesterday\n[01:40.721] Love was such an easy game to play\n[01:45.765] Now I need a place to hide away\n[01:49.493] Oh I believe in yesterday",
