        "fullLyrics": "[00:09.940] I call you'when I need you my hearts on fire\n[00:18.930] You come to me' come to me' wild and wild\n[00:27.730] You come to me' give me everything I need\n[00:37.170] Give me a lifetime of promises and a world of dreams\n[00:46.210] Speak the language of love like you know what it means\n[00:55.380] And it cant be wrong' take my heart and make it strong' baby\n[01:03.960] You're simply the best' better than all the rest'\n[01:13.580] Better than anyone' anyone I've ever met \n[01:22.430] I'm stuck on your heart' I hang on every word you say\n[01:31.930] Tear us apart' baby I would rather be dead\n[01:41.920] In your heart I see the start of every night and every day\n[01:50.980] In your eyes' I get lost' I get washed away\n[01:59.910] Just as long as I'm here in your arms I could be in no better place   \n[02:08.570] You're simply the best' better than all the rest'\n[02:18.120] Better than anyone' anyone I've ever met \n[02:27.110] I'm stuck on your heart' I hang on every word you say\n[02:36.660] Tear us apart' baby I would rather be dead\n[02:47.240] Its the time you leave me I start losing control'\n[02:51.550] You're walking away with my Heart and my soul'\n[02:56.660] I can feel you even when Im alone' oh baby dont let go \n[03:23.070] And you're the best' better than all the rest'\n[03:32.030] Better than anyone' anyone I've ever met \n[03:41.020] I'm stuck on your heart' I hang on every word you say\n[03:51.290] Tear us apart' baby I would rather be dead'\n[04:00.080] Ooh you're the best\n[04:23.809] And you're the best\n[04:27.489] Better than anyone\n[04:32.229] Better than all the rest\n[04:37.669] Better than anyone anyone I've ever met\n[04:41.219] I'm stuck on your heart I hang on every word you say\n[04:59.990] Ooh you're the best   better than anyone",
