        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:26.861] Everything's gonna be alright boys  help is on the way\n[00:38.591] Hold your head up high now  there's no need to cry now\n[00:44.611] We're not running anymore\n[00:48.181] Leave the politics behind boys  they're not working anymore\n[00:54.941] There's so much more at stake here  it's make or break here\n[01:06.231] Haven't we been here before - tell me what we're waiting for\n[01:23.431] Chorus:\n[01:23.871] You gotta remember  you don't have to be afraid\n[01:29.951] You still have the freedom to learn  and say what you wanna say\n[01:33.771] You gotta remember  don't let 'em take away\n[01:41.301] The land we call the home of the brave\n[01:49.761] Who sings the song of the people  you don't hear it anymore\n[01:56.551] I heard it late last summer  to the beat of a different drummer\n[02:07.091] It never sounded quite like that before\n[02:10.961] So you're trying to shake this feeling  that trouble's right outside the door\n[02:19.811] You lie awake each dark night  like a time bomb wound up too tight\n[02:29.691] A storm in waiting  just offshore - tell me what we're waiting for\n[02:46.591] Chorus\n[02:47.151] (Instrumental break)\n[04:08.695] You gotta remember  you don't have to be afraid\n[04:34.655] You still have the freedom to learn  and say what you wanna say\n[04:40.865] You gotta remember  don't let 'em take away\n[04:46.290] The land we call the home of the brave\n[04:52.000] You gotta remember  you don't have to be afraid\n[04:55.580] You still have the freedom to learn  and say what you wanna say\n[05:02.350] You gotta remember  don't let 'em take away\n[05:07.470] The land we call the home of the brave",
