        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:19.460] If I had another chance tonight\n[00:29.390] I'd try to tell you that the things\n[00:34.040] We had were right\n[00:38.100] Time can't erase the love we shared\n[00:44.329] But it gives me time to realize\n[00:49.839] Just how much you cared\n[00:56.979] Now you're gone I'm really not the same\n[01:06.979] I guess I have myself to blame\n[01:15.628] Time can't erase the things we said\n[01:21.878] But it gives me time to realize\n[01:27.108] That you're the one instead\n[01:34.338] You know I won't hold you back now\n[01:43.728] The love we had just can't be found\n[01:53.038] You know I can't hold you back now\n[02:07.358] Now that I'm alone it gives me time\n[02:16.478] To think about the years that you were mine\n[02:26.188] Time can't erase the love we shared\n[02:32.388] But it gives me time to realize\n[02:37.818] Just how much you cared\n[02:44.778] You know I won't hold you back now\n[02:54.138] The love we had just can't be found\n[03:00.638] Listen to me baby\n[03:03.708] You know I can't hold you back now\n[03:55.454] You know I won't hold you back now\n[04:04.614] The love we had just can't be found\n[04:14.014] You know I can't hold you back now\n[04:23.534] The love we had just can't be found\n[04:32.744] You know I can't hold you back now\n[04:42.244] The love we had just can't be found",
