        "fullLyrics": "[00:00.581] Some people live their dreams\n[00:06.881] Some people close their eyes\n[00:11.401] Some people's destiny\n[00:15.911] Passes by\n[00:24.591] There are no guarantees\n[00:26.871] There are no alibis\n[00:36.101] That's how our love must be\n[00:42.251] Don't ask why\n[00:47.871] It takes some time\n[00:52.311] God knows how long\n[00:54.881] I know that I can forget you\n[00:58.731] As soon as my heart stops breaking\n[01:06.571] Anticipating\n[01:12.660] As soon as forever is through\n[01:17.180] I'll be over you\n[01:22.870] Remembering times gone by\n[01:28.740] Promises we once made\n[01:34.580] What are the reasons why\n[01:40.530] Nothing stays the same\n[01:46.410] There were the nights\n[01:50.820] Holding you close\n[01:53.490] Someday I'll try to forget them\n[01:57.580] As soon as my heart stops breaking\n[02:04.960] Anticipating\n[02:12.120] As soon as forever is through\n[02:15.580] I'll be over you\n[02:38.800] As soon as my heart stops breaking\n[02:46.790] Anticipating\n[02:52.400] Someday I'll be over you\n[02:56.320] As soon as my heart stops breaking\n[03:02.260] Anticipating\n[03:10.030] Someday I'll be over you\n[03:13.760] As soon as my heart\n[03:24.830] (as soon as my heart stops breaking)\n[03:28.720] (anticipating)\n[03:31.110] I'll Be over You - Toto",
