        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:39.181] Reflections in my mind  thoughts I can't define\n[00:43.451] My heart is racing and the night goes on\n[00:47.721] I can almost hear a laugh  coming from your photograph\n[00:52.861] Funny how a look can share a thousand meanings\n[00:57.241] Well-intended lies  contemplating alibies\n[01:02.001] Is it really you  or is it me I'm blaming\n[01:06.551] A distant memory flashes over me\n[01:11.181] Even though you're gone  I feel you deep inside\n[01:15.821] Dance beneath the light with that look in your eyes\n[01:23.151] Chorus:\n[01:25.291] I can't stop loving you  time passes quickly and chances are few\n[01:33.001] I won't stop till I'm through loving you  girl\n[01:44.481] There's a window in a heart  I've tried to look through from the start\n[01:48.961] You're never really sure what someone else is thinking\n[01:53.631] Someone's broken something new  another altered point of view\n[01:57.141] Just a certain someone's conscience playing\n[02:03.601] I held it in my hand  I did not understand\n[02:06.421] What lives inside the wind that cries her name\n[02:12.511] Tried to catch a shooting star  what seems so close can't be that far\n[02:16.851] I'm living in a dream that's never ending\n[02:21.631] Dance beneath the light with that look in your eyes\n[02:28.641] Chorus:\n[02:30.641] I can't stop loving you  time passes quickly and chances are few\n[02:39.231] I won't stop till I'm through loving you  girl\n[02:48.801] (Instrumental break)\n[02:49.670] Dancing with that look that's in your eyes\n[03:31.930] Chorus:\n[03:32.380] I can't stop loving you  time passes quickly and chances are few\n[03:40.290] I won't stop till I'm through loving you  girl\n[03:47.300] Chorus:\n[03:49.960] I can't stop loving you  time passes quickly and chances are few\n[04:00.470] I won't stop till I'm through loving you  Loving you",
