        "externalUrl": "",
        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:28.774] I have climbed the highest mountains\n[00:33.318] I have run through the fields\n[00:37.742] Only to be with you\n[00:42.302] Only to be with you\n[00:47.678] I have run I have crawled\n[00:52.142] I have scaled these city walls\n[00:56.982] These city walls\n[01:01.710] Only to be with you\n[01:06.670] But I still haven't found\n[01:11.318] What I'm looking for\n[01:16.150] But I still haven't found\n[01:20.846] What I'm looking for\n[01:25.814] I have kissed honey lips\n[01:30.446] Felt the healing in her finger tips\n[01:34.627] It burned like fire\n[01:39.379] This burning desire\n[01:44.731] I have spoke with the tongue of angels\n[01:49.778] I have held the hand of a devil\n[01:53.866] It was warm in the night\n[01:57.905] I was cold as a stone\n[02:04.121] But I still haven't found\n[02:09.074] What I'm looking for\n[02:13.570] But I still haven't found\n[02:18.114] What I'm looking for\n[02:47.226] I believe in the kingdom come\n[02:51.525] Then all the colours will bleed into one\n[02:55.799] Bleed into one\n[03:00.783] But yes I'm still running\n[03:05.535] You broke the bonds\n[03:07.517] And you loosed the chains\n[03:10.741] Carried the cross of my shame\n[03:14.852] Of my shame you know I believe it\n[03:25.109] But I still haven't found\n[03:29.709] What I'm looking for\n[03:34.533] But I still haven't found\n[03:38.949] What I'm looking for\n[03:44.077] But I still haven't found\n[03:48.581] What I'm looking for\n[03:53.687] But I still haven't found\n[03:57.999] What I'm looking for",
