        "favorite": false,
        "fullLyrics": "[00:27.829] See the stone set in your eyes\n[00:32.129] See the thorn twist in your side\n[00:36.672] I wait for you\n[00:45.290] Sleight of hand and twist of fate\n[00:49.298] On a bed of nails she makes me wait\n[00:53.990] And I wait without you\n[01:00.100] With or without you\n[01:04.544] With or without you\n[01:11.595] Through the storm we reach the shore\n[01:15.426] You give it all but I want more\n[01:20.312] And I'm waiting for you\n[01:26.499] With or without you\n[01:30.826] With or without you\n[01:35.129] I can't live\n[01:39.540] With or without you\n[01:53.317] And you give yourself away\n[01:57.456] And you give yourself away\n[02:01.729] And you give\n[02:03.958] And you give\n[02:06.163] And you give yourself away\n[02:12.366] My hands are tied\n[02:16.429] My body bruised she's got me with\n[02:20.831] Nothing to win and\n[02:24.259] Nothing left to lose\n[02:28.065] And you give yourself away\n[02:32.492] And you give yourself away\n[02:36.779] And you give\n[02:38.911] And you give\n[02:41.101] And you give yourself away\n[02:45.313] With or without you\n[02:49.428] With or without you\n[02:53.637] I can't live\n[02:58.080] With or without you\n[03:20.070] With or without you\n[03:24.341] With or without you\n[03:28.751] I can't live\n[03:33.106] With or without you\n[03:37.413] With or without you",
