        "fullLyrics": "[00:28.610] I get up\n[00:31.850] and nothing gets me down.\n[00:35.960] You got it tough\n[00:38.780] I've seen the toughest around.\n[00:43.400] And I know\n[00:46.220] baby, just how you feel.\n[00:50.780] You've got to roll with the punches to get to what's real\n[00:58.190] Oh can't you see me standing here,\n[01:00.200] I've got my back against the record machine\n[01:04.670] I ain't the worst that you've seen.\n[01:08.510] Oh can't you see what I mean ?\n[01:14.810] Might as well jump. Jump !\n[01:18.410] Might as well jump.\n[01:22.190] Go ahead, jump. Jump !\n[01:25.910] Go ahead, jump.\n[01:27.650] Aaa-ohh Hey you ! How said that ?\n[01:32.840] Baby how you been ?\n[01:36.650] You say you don't know, you won't know\n[01:40.490] until we begin.\n[01:44.690] Well can't you see me standing here,\n[01:46.550] I've got my back against the record machine\n[01:51.020] I ain't the worst that you've seen.\n[01:54.830] Oh can't you see what I mean ?\n[02:01.100] Might as well jump. Jump !\n[02:04.790] Go ahead, jump.\n[02:08.450] Might as well jump. Jump !\n[02:12.200] Go ahead, jump.\n[02:16.250] Jump !\n[03:18.830] Might as well jump. Jump !\n[03:20.270] Go ahead, jump.\n[03:26.240] Get it and jump. Jump !\n[03:29.960] Go ahead, jump\n[03:34.040] Jump !\n[03:45.140] Jump !",
