        "fullLyrics": "[00:14.821] Call me good\n[00:16.441] Call me bad\n[00:18.311] Call me anything you want to baby\n[00:21.871] But I know that you're sad\n[00:25.491] And I know I'll make you happy\n[00:27.370] With the one thing that you never had Baby  I'm your man don't you know that Baby  I'm your man\n[00:43.741] You bet If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me So good\n[00:59.901] You're divine Wanna take you  wanna make you\n[01:04.231] But they tell me it's a crime\n[01:06.101] Everybody knows where the good people go\n[01:09.081] But where we're going baby\n[01:11.451] Ain't no such word as no Baby  I'm your man don't you know who I am Baby  I'm your man\n[01:26.341] You bet If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right - right Do it with me\n[01:42.071] To do it on my own First class information\n[01:45.651] I'll be your sexual inspiration\n[01:49.581] And with some stimulation\n[01:55.261] We can do it right\n[02:11.000] So why waste time\n[02:13.360] With the other guys When you can have mine\n[02:16.740] I ain't ask in' for no sacrifice\n[02:18.100] Baby your friends do not need to know\n[02:22.290] I've got a real nice place to goListen I don't need you to care\n[02:29.921] I don't need you to understand\n[02:33.611] All I want is for you to be there\n[02:36.421] And when I'm turned on\n[02:37.911] If you want me I'm your man If you're gonna do it  do it right  right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right  right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right  right Do it with me If you're gonna do it  do it right  right Do it with me\n[03:08.931] Now listen\n[03:09.551] If you're gonna do it - you know what I say\n[03:13.051] If you're gonna do it don't throw it away\n[03:18.111] Don't throw it baby\n[03:22.821] Because I'll be your boy  I'll be your man\n[03:25.261] I'll be the one who understands\n[03:26.381] I'll be your first  I'll be your last\n[03:28.881] I'll be the only one you ask\n[03:30.991] I'll be your friend  I'll be your toy\n[03:32.561] I'll be the one who brings you joy\n[03:34.491] I'll be your hope  I'll be your pearl\n[03:36.171] I'll take you halfway 'round the world\n[03:40.041] I'll make you rich - I'll make you poor\n[03:45.221] Just don't use the door\n[03:48.891] Do it with me",
