        "fullLyrics": "[00:38.757] I would lock you up but I could not bear to hear you\n[00:42.361] Screaming to be set free\n[00:44.551] I would chain you up if I'd thought you'd swear\n[00:47.551] The only one that mattered was me  me  me\n[00:51.231] I would strap you up but don't worry baby\n[00:54.311] You know I wouldn't hurt you unless you wanted me to\n[00:57.371] It's too late to stop  won't the heavens save me \n[01:00.771] My daddy said  \"The devil looks a lot like you\"\n[01:03.271] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[01:07.201] Tell me that my soul's forgiven\n[01:10.331] Hide you baby's eyes and we can\n[01:16.831] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[01:19.771] One last time might be forever\n[01:23.081] When the passion dies\n[01:25.831] It's just a matter of time before my heart is\n[01:28.701] Looking for a home\n[01:42.031] I'm like a maniac at the end of the day\n[01:44.711] I'm like a doggie barking at your door\n[01:46.651] So come take me back to the place you stay\n[01:50.901] And maybe we can do it once more\n[01:54.401] You say I'm dangerous but don't worry baby\n[01:57.341] I get excited at the things that you do\n[02:00.531] And there's a place for us in a dirty movie\n[02:03.591] 'Cause no-one does it better than me and you\n[02:06.711] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[02:10.221] Tell me that my soul's forgiven\n[02:13.341] Hide your baby's eyes and we can\n[02:16.471] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[02:22.721] One last time might be forever\n[02:25.901] Please don't tell me lies\n[02:28.591] It's just a matter of time before my heart is\n[02:31.471] Looking for a home\n[02:48.444] I ain't got no more worries\n[02:49.404] I'm gonna spend some time with you\n[02:51.024] Loving you takes such courage\n[02:52.774] And don't you think that\n[02:55.654] I know it  I know it  I know it  I know it\n[03:22.600] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[03:25.540] You tell me that my soul's forgiven\n[03:28.740] Hide your baby's eyes and we can  we can  ow\n[03:34.990] You take me to the edge of heaven\n[03:38.120] One last time might be forever\n[03:41.360] Don't you tell me lies because believe me  baby\n[03:45.800] One day you'll wake up on your own\n[04:00.281] I ain't got no more worries\n[04:03.401] I ain't got no more time for you\n[04:06.341] Loving you takes such courage\n[04:09.401] Everyone's got their eyes on you\n[04:12.591] I ain't got no more worries\n[04:15.591] I ain't got no more time for you\n[04:18.651] Loving you takes such courage\n[04:22.091] And don't you think that\n[04:23.721] I know it  I know it  I know it  I know it",
