        "fullLyrics": "[00:22.980] “Here I Go Again”\n[00:23.340] I don't know where I'm goin\n[00:28.290] but I sure know where I've been\n[00:33.450] hanging on the promises in songs of yesterday.\n[00:38.850] An' I've made up my mind' I ain't wasting no more time\n[00:46.500] but here I go again' here I go again.\n[00:49.080] Tho' I keep searching for an answer\n[00:54.060] I never seem to find what I'm looking for.\n[00:59.070] Oh Lord' I pray you give me strength to carry on\n[01:04.710] 'cos I know what it means to walk along the lonely street of dreams.\n[01:14.220] Here I go again on my own\n[01:18.990] goin' down the only road I've ever known.\n[01:24.090] Like a drifter I was born to walk alone.\n[01:30.480] An' I've made up my mind' I ain't wasting no more time.\n[01:40.650] Just another heart in need of rescue\n[01:45.750] waiting on love's sweet charity\n[01:51.000] an' I'm gonna hold on for the rest of my days\n[01:56.340] 'cos I know what it means to walk along the lonely street of dreams.\n[02:05.670] Here I go again on my own\n[02:10.620] goin' down the only road I've ever known.\n[02:15.720] Like a hobo I was born to walk alone.\n[02:22.170] An' I've made up my mind' I ain't wasting no more time\n[02:30.000] but here I go again' here I go again'\n[02:40.560] here I go again' here I go.\n[02:45.810] 'cos I know what it means to walk along the lonely street of dreams.\n[02:47.700] Here I go again on my own\n[02:48.330] goin' down the only road I've ever known.\n[02:50.100] Like a drifter I was born to walk alone.\n[03:06.090] An' I've made up my mind' I ain't wasting no more time\n[03:15.570] Here I go again on my own\n[03:20.340] goin' down the only road I've ever known.\n[03:25.440] Like a drifter I was born to walk alone.\n[03:31.860] 'cos I know what it means to walk along the lonely street of dreams.\n[03:41.400] Here I go again on my own\n[03:46.170] goin' down the only road I've ever known.\n[03:48.960] Like a drifter I was born to walk alone.",
